(2647250,"The Journey&apos;s End",69956,"<p>The world celebrates the Demon King&apos;s defeat at the hands of the Hero and his companions. Now that their great adventure is over, what will Frieren the mage do next?</p>",1,1,30,"2023-09-29","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264161.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2647250/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x01-the-journeys-end"),
(2655203,"It Didn&apos;t Have to Be Magic...",69956,"<p>Frieren instructs Fern in the use of magic while deciphering a grimoire for Heiter.</p>",2,1,30,"2023-09-29","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264162.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655203/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x02-it-didnt-have-to-be-magic"),
(2655204,"Killing Magic",69956,"<p>While retracing the path she took on her adventure with her former traveling companions, Frieren confronts an old enemy.</p>",3,1,30,"2023-09-29","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264165.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655204/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x03-killing-magic"),
(2655205,"The Land Where Souls Rest",69956,"<p>Frieren and Fern pay a visit to Eisen, who requests their help in finding the notes of Flamme the Legendary Mage.</p>",4,1,30,"2023-09-29","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264166.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655205/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x04-the-land-where-souls-rest"),
(2655224,"Phantoms of the Dead",69956,"<p>Frieren and Fern investigate ghost sightings at a village where people have started going missing.</p>",5,1,30,"2023-10-06","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264167.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655224/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x05-phantoms-of-the-dead"),
(2655225,"The Hero of the Village",69956,"<p>Frieren and Fern enlist Stark&apos;s help to fight the solar dragon - but is he up to the task?</p>",6,1,30,"2023-10-13","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264168.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655225/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x06-the-hero-of-the-village"),
(2655226,"Like a Fairy Tale",69956,"<p>After reflecting on the transient nature of the past as it exists in people&apos;s collective memories, Frieren unexpectedly runs into a sworn enemy.</p>",7,1,30,"2023-10-20","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264169.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655226/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x07-like-a-fairy-tale"),
(2655227,"Frieren the Slayer",69956,"<p>As tensions in Graf Granat&apos;s domain reach a breaking point, Fern and Stark find their own resolve - and Frieren resumes an old duty.</p>",8,1,30,"2023-10-27","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264170.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655227/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x08-frieren-the-slayer"),
(2655228,"Aura the Guillotine",69956,"<p>While Fern and Stark make a temporary retreat with Graf Granat, Frieren&apos;s true foe awaits her outside the city.</p>",9,1,30,"2023-11-03","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264174.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655228/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x09-aura-the-guillotine"),
(2655229,"A Powerful Mage",69956,"<p>Frieren&apos;s many years of training under her teacher Flamme are tested in her confrontation with Aura the Guillotine. Will Aura&apos;s scales find her wanting?</p>",10,1,30,"2023-11-10","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264175.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655229/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x10-a-powerful-mage"),
(2655230,"Winter in the Northern Lands",69956,"<p>Frieren and her companions continue their journey through the northern lands, but obstacles both natural and manmade still stand in their way.</p>",11,1,30,"2023-11-17","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264176.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655230/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x11-winter-in-the-northern-lands"),
(2655231,"A Real Hero",69956,"<p>Deep in the mountains of the northern lands, Frieren and her party arrive at the Village of the Sword, where they have another job to do.</p>",12,1,30,"2023-11-24","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264251.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655231/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x12-a-real-hero"),
(2655232,"Aversion to One&apos;s Own Kind",69956,"<p>While passing by a village in the woods of the northern lands, Frieren and party meet Sein, a gifted priest who is nonetheless corrupt enough to give even Heiter a run for his money. But what happened in his past?</p>",13,1,30,"2023-12-01","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264252.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655232/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x13-aversion-to-ones-own-kind"),
(2655233,"Privilege of the Young",69956,"<p>The party arrives in a large and lively town with a bustling shopping district that Frieren once visited with Himmel, but something seems to have come up between Fern and Stark.</p>",14,1,30,"2023-12-08","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264253.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655233/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x14-privilege-of-the-young"),
(2655234,"Smells Like Trouble",69956,"<p>When the party happens upon a town whose inhabitants are all mysteriously asleep, it&apos;s time for their newest traveling companion to prove his mettle.</p>",15,1,30,"2023-12-15","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264254.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655234/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x15-smells-like-trouble"),
(2655235,"Long-Lived Friends",69956,"<p>Frieren pays a visit to Old Man Voll, a long-lived friend of hers, with traveling companions in tow.</p>",16,1,30,"2023-12-22","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264255.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655235/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x16-long-lived-friends"),
(2655236,"Take Care",69956,"<p>Now that Sein finally has a lead on the whereabouts of his long-lost friend, is it time for him and Frieren&apos;s party to part ways?</p>",17,1,30,"2024-01-05","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264172.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655236/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x17-take-care"),
(2655237,"First-Class Mage Exam",69956,"<p>Frieren and party finally arrive in Äußerst, ready to undergo the first-class mage exam, and meet a number of colorful characters who are there to do the same.</p>",18,1,30,"2024-01-12","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264256.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655237/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x18-first-class-mage-exam"),
(2655238,"Well-Laid Plans",69956,"<p>Frieren and her new teammates hatch a plan to capture a Stille - but are the other teams just going to stand by and let it happen?</p>",19,1,30,"2024-01-19","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/505/1264257.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2655238/frieren-beyond-journeys-end-1x19-well-laid-plans"),
