(86778,"To You, in 2000 Years - The Fall of Shiganshina (1)",919,"<p>For over a century, humans have been living in settlements surrounded by gigantic walls, which prevent the Titans, giant humanoid creatures who eat humans, from entering. Young Eren Yeager wishes to see the outside world by joining the Recon Corps, as he likens living in the cities to livestock. Despite this, his foster sister Mikasa Ackerman and their mother Carla are against him in joining the Corps. Even after seeing the Recon Corps returning home with large casualties, Eren expresses his interest to join.</p>",1,1,25,"2013-04-07","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/97/242650.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/86778/attack-on-titan-1x01-to-you-in-2000-years-the-fall-of-shiganshina-1"),
(86779,"That Day - The Fall of Shiganshina (2)",919,"<p>Some of the Shiganshina townsfolk escape to the inner Wall Maria while the soldiers try to hold off the Titans. The soldiers try to close the gate, but one of the Titans rams the gate, breaching Wall Maria, and causing those inside to retreat even further to Wall Rose. During the next year, as a food shortage becomes apparent, the government orders the refugees to work at the farms or fight to reclaim Wall Maria.</p>",2,1,25,"2013-04-14","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/97/242651.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/86779/attack-on-titan-1x02-that-day-the-fall-of-shiganshina-2"),
(86780,"A Dim Light Amid Despair - Humanity&apos;s Comeback (1)",919,"<p>Eren begins his training with the Cadet Corps, but questions about his painful past overwhelm him. When he struggles with a maneuvering exercise, Berholt and Reiner offer kindly advice.</p>",3,1,25,"2013-04-21","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/97/242652.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/86780/attack-on-titan-1x03-a-dim-light-amid-despair-humanitys-comeback-1"),
(86781,"The Night of the Closing Ceremony - Humanity&apos;s Comeback (2)",919,"<p>Annie proves her skill in a sparring session, Jan dreams of serving alongside the King, and graduation day brings shocking revelations - along with a sudden outbreak of violence.</p>",4,1,25,"2013-04-28","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/543/1357583.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/86781/attack-on-titan-1x04-the-night-of-the-closing-ceremony-humanitys-comeback-2"),
