(2028,"Tactical Village",49,"<p>The precinct heads to Tactical Village Day, a mandatory training course in which all regional precincts compete. While there, Amy runs into Teddy, a fellow officer she used to date. Meanwhile, Holt becomes addicted to a game on his phone and Rosa is pissed at Charles for not inviting her to his wedding.</p>",19,1,30,"2014-03-04","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015875.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2028/brooklyn-nine-nine-1x19-tactical-village"),
(2029,"Fancy Brudgom",49,"<p>Charles asks Jake to be the best man at his wedding, a role that requires Jake to be supportive in important wedding decisions, ranging from cake tasting to floral arrangements. Meanwhile, Terry, Amy and Gina support each other as they start a new extreme diet and Holt helps Rosa make a sincere apology.</p>",20,1,30,"2014-03-11","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015876.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2029/brooklyn-nine-nine-1x20-fancy-brudgom"),
(2030,"Unsolvable",49,"<p>When Jake gets the weekend off, he decides to take on a cold case that everyone thinks is unsolvable, but with the help of Terry, the two try to crack the case once and for all. Meanwhile, Amy plans a romantic trip with Teddy and Gina and Rosa let Charles in on one of their best-kept secrets.</p>",21,1,30,"2014-03-18","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015877.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2030/brooklyn-nine-nine-1x21-unsolvable"),
(2031,"Charges and Specs",49,"<p>Jake&apos;s investigation of philanthropic civic leader Lucas Wint is shut down by Commissioner Podalski. Still determined to crack the case, Jake enlists Amy and a reluctant Captain Holt to help him uncover more evidence, even if it means facing suspension. Meanwhile, Charles is devastated over pre-marital problems with Vivian, and Gina knows just how to cheer him up.</p>",22,1,30,"2014-03-25","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015878.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2031/brooklyn-nine-nine-1x22-charges-and-specs"),
(2032,"Undercover",49,"<p>Jake&apos;s undercover FBI operation ends in a successful sting, until he learns one mobster has gotten away. As Jake enlists Charles&apos; help to track him down, Holt tests the squad&apos;s patience with practice drills.</p>",1,2,30,"2014-09-28","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015880.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2032/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x01-undercover"),
(2033,"Chocolate Milk",49,"<p>Holt is taken by surprise when his longtime nemesis, Deputy Chief Madeline Wuntch arrives for an inspection of his precinct. Meanwhile, Jake and Terry test the boundaries of &quot;work friends&quot; vs. &quot;friend friends&quot; as they investigate a stabbing at a hipster chocolate milk bar.</p>",2,2,30,"2014-10-05","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015881.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2033/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x02-chocolate-milk"),
(2034,"The Jimmy Jab Games",49,"<p>The squad has time to kill when the arrival of the Serbian President&apos;s motorcade to Brooklyn has been delayed. So, Jake launches &quot;The Jimmy Jab Games,&quot; an annual series of competitions in the precinct. Meanwhile, Terry and Holt take on a new drug task force approved by Holt&apos;s nemesis, Deputy Chief Madeline Wuntch.</p>",3,2,30,"2014-10-12","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015882.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2034/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x03-the-jimmy-jab-games"),
(14051,"Halloween II",49,"<p>The Peralta/Holt annual Halloween bet continues when Jake challenges the Captain that he can steal his watch before midnight. Meanwhile, Gina is upset that her dance team, Floorgasm, kicks her off the squad and Terry confronts her about her bad attitude.</p>",4,2,30,"2014-10-19","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015883.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/14051/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x04-halloween-ii"),
(14052,"The Mole",49,"<p>There&apos;s a mole in the precinct and Holt and Jake need to find out who it is before Deputy Chief Madeline Wuntch gets wind of it. Meanwhile, Terry and Rosa visit a &quot;silent&quot; disco to uncover new leads for their new drug task force.</p>",5,2,30,"2014-11-02","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015884.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/14052/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x05-the-mole"),
(14545,"Jake and Sophia",49,"<p>Jake hits it off with Sophia, a woman whom he meets at a bar, only to find out she is the defense attorney for a perp he is trying to put in jail. Meanwhile, Gina and Charles work to put their relationship behind them.</p>",6,2,30,"2014-11-09","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015885.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/14545/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x06-jake-and-sophia"),
(39443,"Lockdown",49,"<p>The precinct goes into lockdown mode on Thanksgiving night, and Jake, who was left in charge, is confident in his ability to keep spirits high and avoid chaos. Amy is less confident, as things spiral out of control.</p>",7,2,30,"2014-11-16","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015886.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/39443/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x07-lockdown"),
(39444,"USPIS",49,"<p>While attempting to catch a drug dealer, Jake and Charles reluctantly join forces with the nerdy lead investigator at the U.S. Postal Service, Jack Danger. Meanwhile, the rest of the team helps Amy quit smoking.</p>",8,2,30,"2014-11-23","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015887.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/39444/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x08-uspis"),
(44365,"The Road Trip",49,"<p>In an attempt to add a touch of romance to their work trip, Jake invites his girlfriend, Sophia, as well as Amy&apos;s boyfriend, Teddy, to join them at a B&amp;B. Meanwhile, Rosa adamantly refuses to admit to Terry and Gina that she is sick, and Charles is eager to help Holt with his anniversary breakfast.</p>",9,2,30,"2014-11-30","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015888.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/44365/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x09-the-road-trip"),
(45777,"The Pontiac Bandit Returns",49,"<p>Aka Doug Judy, is back in custody, after jamming up Jake and Rosa in his previous encounter with them. But when Rosa discovers that Judy knows the whereabouts of the &quot;Giggle Pig&quot; drug leader, Capt. Holt offers the perp a plea deal to help track down the drug kingpin. Meanwhile, Gina and Boyle are nervous that their parents might be getting too close, and Santiago makes Holt a Christmas gift against his wishes.</p>",10,2,30,"2014-12-07","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015889.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/45777/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x10-the-pontiac-bandit-returns"),
(50183,"Stakeout",49,"<p>Jake and Charles&apos; bro-mance starts to crack when they volunteer for an eight-day stakeout in very close quarters. Meanwhile, Captain Holt&apos;s nephew, Marcus, comes to Brooklyn and captures Rosa&apos;s attention.</p>",11,2,30,"2014-12-14","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015890.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/50183/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x11-stakeout"),
(58257,"Beach House",49,"<p>The team is excited to spend the weekend at Charles&apos; beach house for a detectives-only-getaway, until Jake ruins the fun by inviting Captain Holt. Meanwhile, Charles helps Rosa send romantic texts to her new boyfriend, and Gina tries to get Amy drunk, simply for her own enjoyment.</p>",12,2,30,"2015-01-04","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015891.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/58257/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x12-beach-house"),
(92045,"Payback",49,"<p>The squad decides it&apos;s high time Jake paid them back all the money he has owed them from over the years. Meanwhile, Amy and Holt team up to re-open the Brooklyn Broiler case.</p>",13,2,30,"2015-01-11","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015892.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/92045/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x13-payback"),
(108510,"Defense Rests",49,"<p>When Sophia&apos;s job gets in the way of her relationship with Jake, Jake tries to smooth things over with her boss. Meanwhile, Wuntch needs Holt&apos;s help for a job recommendation.</p>",14,2,30,"2015-01-25","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015893.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/108510/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x14-defense-rests"),
(117726,"Windbreaker City",49,"<p>Jake is heartbroken over Sophia, but his spirits are lifted when the squad is invited to a Homeland Security terrorist training simulation. That is, until the agent in charge assigns them the lame role of playing hostages. Meanwhile, Gina administers a psychological exam to Holt, and Amy and Rosa compete for a day off from work.</p>",15,2,30,"2015-02-08","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015894.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/117726/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x15-windbreaker-city"),
(122944,"The Wednesday Incident",49,"<p>When Jake notices that Holt has been acting moody, he teams up with Holt&apos;s husband to figure out what happened. Meanwhile, at the precinct, Charles tries to get a confession out of a geriatric suspect who pretends to be senile and adorable whenever Amy and Rosa are around.</p>",16,2,30,"2015-02-15","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015895.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/122944/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x16-the-wednesday-incident"),
(128944,"Boyle-Linetti Wedding",49,"<p>It&apos;s the day of Gina and Charles&apos; parents&apos; wedding, and the whole squad is given a job to fulfill for the ceremony. However, Jake and Amy get sidetracked chasing a criminal, and Terry struggles to officiate the wedding.</p>",17,2,30,"2015-03-01","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015896.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/128944/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x17-boyle-linetti-wedding"),
(139657,"Captain Peralta",49,"<p>Jake&apos;s mainly absentee father, Roger, comes to town to spend some time with his son. Jake can&apos;t wait to see him, but Charles is skeptical of Roger&apos;s intentions. Meanwhile, Holt tasks Amy, Terry, Gina and Rosa with an impossible brain teaser in exchange for Beyoncé tickets.</p>",18,2,30,"2015-03-08","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015897.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/139657/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x18-captain-peralta"),
(141513,"Sabotage",49,"<p>After a streak of really bad luck, Jake thinks he&apos;s being sabotaged by an enemy. Holt assigns Amy and Rosa to investigate the truth. Meanwhile, Holt hurts Gina&apos;s feelings by calling her dance troupe a &quot;hobby,&quot; and Charles is stuck working a case with Scully and Hitchcock in Jake&apos;s absence.</p>",19,2,30,"2015-03-15","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015898.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/141513/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x19-sabotage"),
(144419,"AC/DC",49,"<p>After Jake injures himself on a case, Terry forces him take time off and rest - something Jake doesn&apos;t know how to do. Across town, Holt and Rosa try to avoid intimate conversation during a double-date with their significant others.</p>",20,2,30,"2015-04-26","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015899.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/144419/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x20-acdc"),
(144420,"Det. Dave Majors",49,"<p>Jake is excited to work a case with the best detective in the NYPD, Detective Majors, until Majors shares his intentions to ask Amy out on a date. Meanwhile, Charles and Gina try to convince Terry to stay at the Nine-Nine when he considers accepting an offer to work at a private security firm.</p>",21,2,30,"2015-05-03","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015900.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/144420/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x21-det-dave-majors"),
(144421,"The Chopper",49,"<p>Holt is wary when Wuntch lets Jake work his dream case, worried that she is setting him up to fail. Back at the precinct, Amy, Rosa and Gina help Terry host a field trip for a local magnet school.</p>",22,2,30,"2015-05-10","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015901.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/144421/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x22-the-chopper"),
(151671,"Johnny and Dora",49,"<p>Jake and Amy go undercover to catch Brooklyn&apos;s most notorious identity thief, and the case brings them closer together - very close. Meanwhile, the entire precinct is caught off-guard when one of their own says goodbye to the Nine-Nine.</p>",23,2,30,"2015-05-17","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015902.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/151671/brooklyn-nine-nine-2x23-johnny-and-dora"),
(182392,"New Captain",49,"<p>After Holt is transferred to the NYPD Department of Public Relations, the new captain&apos;s arrival causes the precinct to dissolve into chaos, despite Terry&apos;s best efforts to keep everyone on point. Meanwhile, Jake and Amy face the aftermath of their &quot;for reals&quot; kiss.</p>",1,3,30,"2015-09-27","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015906.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/182392/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x01-new-captain"),
(185606,"The Funeral",49,"<p>The Nine-Nine gets another personnel change that could put Jake and Amy&apos;s budding relationship at risk. Meanwhile, Terry assists Holt with an important public relations matter, and Rosa and Gina try to convince Charles to rethink his affection for a fellow officer.</p>",2,3,30,"2015-10-04","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015907.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/185606/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x02-the-funeral"),
(236848,"Boyle&apos;s Hunch",49,"<p>Jake thinks Boyle might have met his soulmate in Genevieve, an art gallery owner, and he tries to help set them up. Meanwhile, Rosa deals with inter-precinct theft and Holt seeks Amy&apos;s help with an image campaign.</p>",3,3,30,"2015-10-11","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015908.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/236848/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x03-boyles-hunch"),
(277905,"The Oolong Slayer",49,"<p>When investigating a serial killer, Jake enlists Holt&apos;s help in an attempt to solve the case off the radar. At the precinct, Rosa and Amy are forced to deal with demands from an old adversary and Terry discovers a new obsession.</p>",4,3,30,"2015-10-18","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015909.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/277905/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x04-the-oolong-slayer"),
(313290,"Halloween, Part III",49,"<p>The third installment of Captain Holt and Jake&apos;s Halloween heist culminates with a tie-breaking competition to claim the title of &quot;amazing detective slash genius.&quot; This year, Jake and Holt split the squad into two teams to help them win.</p>",5,3,30,"2015-10-25","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015910.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/313290/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x05-halloween-part-iii"),
(378141,"Into the Woods",49,"<p>Jake and Charles convince Terry to take a weekend camping trip as a much needed &quot;babymoon,&quot; but they soon realize it might not be the idealistic weekend for which they had hoped. Meanwhile back at the precinct, Holt gives Rosa some important relationship advice and Amy enlists Gina&apos;s help to prepare her for an important presentation.</p>",6,3,30,"2015-11-08","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015911.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/378141/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x06-into-the-woods"),
(385062,"The Mattress",49,"<p>Jake and Amy convince the Captain to let them work a case together involving a new street drug, but their new relationship gets in the way. Meanwhile, at the precinct, Charles panics when he realizes he&apos;s damaged one of Holt&apos;s prized possessions and Terry teaches Rosa a lesson in discipline.</p>",7,3,30,"2015-11-15","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015912.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/385062/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x07-the-mattress"),
(2035,"Ava",49,"<p>Jake&apos;s in charge of entertaining Sharon while Terry and Rosa head off to learn about the Douglass Street murders, but Sharon&apos;s water breaks and crisis ensues at the precinct; and Amy and Charles must process paperwork by hand due to an internet outage. Meanwhile, Holt is forced to confront his ex-boyfriend.</p>",8,3,30,"2015-11-22","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015913.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2035/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x08-ava"),
(443338,"The Swedes",49,"<p>In an attempt to solve an international case, Jake and Rosa are forced to work with a pair of Swedish cops and things get very competitive, very quickly. Meanwhile, Amy and Terry offer to help Gina prepare for a big test and Holt enlists Charles to sub in as his squash partner for an annual tournament.</p>",9,3,30,"2015-12-06","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015914.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/443338/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x09-the-swedes"),
