(529664,"Hostage Situation",49,"<p>Charles and Genevieve want to take their relationship to a new level, but his ex-wife, Eleanor, steamrolls their plans. Meanwhile, Amy asks Terry to write a recommendation letter with disastrous results, and Holt and Rosa enlist Gina&apos;s help to solve a case.</p>",11,3,30,"2016-01-05","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015916.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/529664/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x11-hostage-situation"),
(550601,"9 Days",49,"<p>When Captain Holt and Jake accidentally contract the mumps during an investigation, they decide to be quarantined together in hopes of still solving the case. Meanwhile, Rosa tries to help Boyle through a mourning process, and Terry is forced to clean up Hitchcock and Scully&apos;s mess.</p>",12,3,30,"2016-01-19","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015917.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/550601/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x12-9-days"),
(558571,"The Cruise",49,"<p>Jake and Amy are excited to go on their first real vacation together, but Amy&apos;s perfectly planned cruise ship itinerary is thwarted when they discover an old adversary is on board with them. Meanwhile, Gina and Terry help Captain Holt survive a visit from his sister, Debbie, and Charles and Rosa vie for the same apartment.</p>",13,3,30,"2016-01-26","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015918.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/558571/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x13-the-cruise"),
(563475,"Karen Peralta",49,"<p>On his birthday, Jake brings Amy to meet his mother, but a surprise appearance by his dad throws a wrench in his special day. Meanwhile, Rosa and Charles struggle with a new mandate regarding body cams while on a stakeout with Terry, and Gina forgets to inform the precinct about an important plan of Holt&apos;s.</p>",14,3,30,"2016-02-02","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015919.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/563475/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x14-karen-peralta"),
(573792,"The 9-8",49,"<p>The Nine-Nine host the detectives from the Nine-Eight, their neighboring precinct, reuniting Jake with his old partner. Charles is immediately jealous and tries to reclaim his best friend status with Jake. Meanwhile, the rest of the precinct tries to be welcoming to the Nine-Eight, but it doesn&apos;t go as well as they had planned.</p>",15,3,30,"2016-02-09","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015920.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/573792/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x15-the-9-8"),
(589447,"House Mouses",49,"<p>When Jake insults Hitchcock and Scully&apos;s work ethic in the precinct, they force their way into one of his cases in attempt to prove themselves. Meanwhile, Amy and Gina help Rosa conquer one of her biggest fears, and Holt and Boyle work a celebrity case.</p>",16,3,30,"2016-02-16","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015921.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/589447/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x16-house-mouses"),
(594135,"Adrian Pimento",49,"<p>When an unstable detective returns to the Nine-Nine after years undercover, Jake doesn&apos;t know what to make of him. Meanwhile, Charles&apos; rebellious behavior pits him against the precinct&apos;s custodian, and Holt enlists Gina&apos;s help in directing a &quot;fun and informational&quot; video starring himself and Rosa.</p>",17,3,30,"2016-02-23","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015922.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/594135/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x17-adrian-pimento"),
(608802,"Cheddar",49,"<p>Holt allows Amy and Jake to house-sit for him while he visits Kevin in Paris, but mayhem ensues when Holt&apos;s beloved dog, Cheddar, goes missing under their watch. Meanwhile, a romantic fling between Adrian Pimento and Rosa disrupts Terry and the rest of the precinct.</p>",18,3,30,"2016-03-01","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015923.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/608802/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x18-cheddar"),
(622396,"Terry Kitties",49,"<p>In an attempt to prove to his old precinct that he&apos;s not a joke, Terry enlists Jake&apos;s help in solving a case from his past. Meanwhile, Adrian moves in with Charles, with mixed results, and Amy invites herself to a hyper-competitive training exercise with Holt and Rosa.</p>",19,3,30,"2016-03-15","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015924.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/622396/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x19-terry-kitties"),
(636787,"Paranoia",49,"<p>Rosa enlists Jake to help change Terry&apos;s disapproving opinion about her fast-moving relationship with Adrian Pimento. But their love for each other is put on hold when Pimento thinks someone from his past is trying to kill him.</p>",20,3,30,"2016-03-29","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015925.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/636787/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x20-paranoia"),
(636788,"Maximum Security",49,"<p>In an attempt to get information on a criminal operation, Amy has to go undercover at a women&apos;s prison and befriend one of the prisoners. Meanwhile back at the precinct, Holt and the team plan a fake funeral in an attempt to catch a hitman.</p>",21,3,30,"2016-04-05","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015926.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/636788/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x21-maximum-security"),
(636789,"The Bureau",49,"<p>With Pimento&apos;s life still in peril, Captain Holt calls on an old friend in the FBI to help with a seemingly impossible heist. Meanwhile Amy makes a breakthrough while undercover, and Terry and Gina discover an information leak in the Nine-Nine.</p>",22,3,30,"2016-04-12","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015927.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/636789/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x22-the-bureau"),
(636790,"Greg and Larry",49,"<p>After a surprising turn of events in the Nine-Nine&apos;s attempt to track down Adrian Pimento&apos;s hitman, the precinct drops everything when they suspect Holt is in danger.</p>",23,3,30,"2016-04-19","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015928.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/636790/brooklyn-nine-nine-3x23-greg-and-larry"),
(835409,"Coral Palms, Part 1",49,"<p>Jake and Holt remain in Florida, adjusting to their new lives under the Witness Protection Program, while Jimmy &quot;The Butcher&quot; Figgis is still on the loose. Their one human link to their regular lives is U.S. Marshall Karen Haas, but their anonymity may be in danger...</p>",1,4,30,"2016-09-20","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015930.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/835409/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x01-coral-palms-part-1"),
(895548,"Coral Palms, Part 2",49,"<p>After Jimmy &quot;The Butcher&quot; Figgis sees Jake and Holt&apos;s viral video, the two begin plotting their attack. However, they are forced to experience the other side of the interrogation table when caught red-handed. Back at the precinct, a questionable new Captain takes over.</p>",2,4,30,"2016-09-27","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015931.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/895548/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x02-coral-palms-part-2"),
(895549,"Coral Palms, Part 3",49,"<p>The team makes a road trip to Florida to try to help Jake and Holt take down Figgis. With an unforeseen injury and yet another interruption by Sheriff Reynolds, the plan doesn&apos;t follow through quite like they all had hoped. In the midst of the chaos, Jake and Amy share an awkward reunion.</p>",3,4,30,"2016-10-04","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015932.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/895549/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x03-coral-palms-part-3"),
(893359,"The Night Shift",49,"<p>As Jake struggles with his first case back at the precinct, he encounters Jess Day, who is visiting New York, and enlists her to help him find his suspect. Meanwhile, Holt researches ways to increase office morale and Amy tries to figure out why Rosa keeps taking such long breaks.</p>",4,4,30,"2016-10-11","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015933.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/893359/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x04-the-night-shift"),
(944750,"Halloween IV",49,"<p>It&apos;s Halloween in the Nine-Nine, which can only mean one thing: heist time. This year, the squad members pull out all the stops in their quest to win the new defending title of &quot;Ultimate Detective Slash Genius.&quot; Lines are drawn and plans are made, but there can only be one reigning champion</p>",5,4,30,"2016-10-18","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015934.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/944750/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x05-halloween-iv"),
(974745,"Monster in the Closet",49,"<p>Pimento and Rosa decide to pick up where they left off and get married, so the whole squad preps a perfect wedding under Amy&apos;s careful direction. Pimento enlists Jake and Gina to hunt for his grandmother&apos;s ruby earrings for Rosa to wear in the ceremony, but the universe has other plans for them.</p>",6,4,30,"2016-11-15","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015935.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/974745/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x06-monster-in-the-closet"),
(979324,"Mr. Santiago",49,"<p>At Amy&apos;s intricately planned Thanksgiving dinner, Jake goes &quot;full Santiago&quot; (binder and all) in order to impress her father, a former cop. With Jake and Amy&apos;s focus elsewhere, Charles is left on turkey duty and Holt helps Pimento cope after learning he can no longer work for the NYPD.</p>",7,4,30,"2016-11-22","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015936.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/979324/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x07-mr-santiago"),
(979805,"Skyfire Cycle",49,"<p>When famous author DC Parlov receives death threats, Jake and Terry take the case, so that Terry can meet his lifelong hero. Back at the precinct, Gina forces her way into the Boyle clan of cousins in an attempt to choose the location of the annual Boyle family vacation. Meanwhile, Holt&apos;s anger peaks when Amy chooses Kevin&apos;s side in their argument about a math puzzle.</p>",8,4,30,"2016-11-29","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015937.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/979805/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x08-skyfire-cycle"),
(952563,"The Overmining",49,"<p>Captain &quot;CJ&quot; is having major problems with a big case, and Jake and Holt find the motivation to help him out. Inside the precinct, war ensues when Terry enforces a green initiative and tells Gina to get rid of her precious space heater, while Rosa and Boyle take a break from the night shift to visit a foot massage parlor.</p>",9,4,30,"2016-12-06","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015938.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/952563/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x09-the-overmining"),
(986268,"Captain Latvia",49,"<p>Charles enlists Jake&apos;s help in tracking down his son&apos;s favorite toy for Christmas, and the pair finds themselves accidentally facing off against a Latvian criminal ring as a result. Back at the precinct, the team gears up for their annual Christmas carol competition against their sworn enemy: the MTA.</p>",10,4,30,"2016-12-13","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015939.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/986268/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x10-captain-latvia"),
(1007920,"The Fugitive, Part 1",49,"<p>A mass escape of convicts from a prison van in the streets of Brooklyn sends the entire squad on a manhunt. The only key witness? Former NFL running back Marshawn Lynch. Meanwhile, Jake and Amy place a bet on who can bring in the most escaped convicts - and the loser has to move into the winner&apos;s apartment. Then, with only one fugitive still on the loose, Jake enlists a surprising ally.</p>",11,4,30,"2017-01-01","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015940.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1007920/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x11-the-fugitive-part-1"),
(1008010,"The Fugitive, Part 2",49,"<p>With only one fugitive left on the loose after a mass escape of convicts from a prison van in the streets of Brooklyn that sent the entire squad on a manhunt, Jake enlists a surprising ally.</p>",12,4,30,"2017-01-01","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015941.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1008010/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x12-the-fugitive-part-2"),
(1038751,"The Audit",49,"<p>With the crime rate lowered, Brooklyn will be shutting down one of its precincts – permanently. The Nine-Nine is confident they will be evaluated fairly, until the official auditor turns out to be Amy&apos;s ex-boyfriend, Teddy. The whole squad then must band together to try to save the precinct.</p>",13,4,30,"2017-04-11","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015942.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1038751/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x13-the-audit"),
(1096395,"Serve & Protect",49,"<p>Terry&apos;s ex replaces Teddy in evaluating the precinct, but Jake and Rosa are distracted by a burglary case that occurred on the set of one of their favorite detective TV shows. As the rest of the Nine-Nine concentrate on the audit (and Terry&apos;s past relationship strategies), Jake and Rosa pass time with the series star and producer, who meddle in the case and charm Jake with the glamour of show business.</p>",14,4,30,"2017-04-18","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015943.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1096395/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x14-serve-protect"),
(1096396,"The Last Ride",49,"<p>In what could be their last case as partners, Jake and Charles go to great extremes to apprehend a local bike thief. Terry shockingly isn&apos;t in the lead for &quot;Mr. Nine-Nine&quot; (the detective who has solved the most cases), leaving Rosa determined to boost his ego. Meanwhile, Amy spends some precious time with Holt.</p>",15,4,30,"2017-04-25","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015944.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1096396/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x15-the-last-ride"),
(1096398,"Moo Moo",49,"<p>Sergeant Jeffords is stopped by a fellow police officer while off-duty in his own neighborhood. When the incident escalates, Terry wants to file an official complaint against him, but Captain Holt has other ideas. Meanwhile, Jake and Amy get a glimpse into the difficulties of parenthood and answer some tough questions when they babysit Terry&apos;s kids.</p>",16,4,30,"2017-05-02","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015945.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1096398/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x16-moo-moo"),
(1053163,"Cop-Con",49,"<p>The precinct packs up and heads to the Tri-State Police Officers&apos; annual Cop-Con, which is usually the Nine-Nine&apos;s excuse for a big annual party. But the squad&apos;s fun is threatened this year when Holt asks them to be on their best behavior. Then, Amy suddenly vanishes hours before taking the Sergeant Exam, and it&apos;s up to Jake and Rosa to find her before it&apos;s too late.</p>",17,4,30,"2017-05-09","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015946.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1053163/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x17-cop-con"),
(1096399,"Chasing Amy",49,"<p>Amy suddenly vanishes hours before taking the Sergeant Exam, and it&apos;s up to Jake and Rosa to find her before it&apos;s too late.</p>",18,4,30,"2017-05-09","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015947.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1096399/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x18-chasing-amy"),
(1096400,"Your Honor",49,"<p>Captain Holt&apos;s mom seeks support from the precinct after her house is robbed. Meanwhile, Terry, Rosa and Boyle remodel the breakroom and Amy teaches Gina how to change her own car tire. </p>",19,4,30,"2017-05-16","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015948.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1096400/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x19-your-honor"),
(1096401,"The Slaughterhouse",49,"<p>Jake and Rosa try to earn the respect of their idol; Charles, Terry and Gina try to resolve Scully and Hitchcock&apos;s conflict.</p>",20,4,30,"2017-05-16","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015949.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1096401/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x20-the-slaughterhouse"),
(1096402,"The Bank Job",49,"<p>As Jake and Rosa continue their search for a bank-robbing operation with Lieutenant Hawkins, they realize there&apos;s more to her team than meets the eye.</p>",21,4,30,"2017-05-23","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015950.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1096402/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x21-the-bank-job"),
(1096403,"Crime and Punishment",49,"<p>Jake and Rosa are framed for a crime they didn&apos;t commit, it&apos;s up to the Nine-Nine to find a way to bust them out.</p>",22,4,30,"2017-05-23","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015951.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1096403/brooklyn-nine-nine-4x22-crime-and-punishment"),
(1223230,"The Big House, Part 1",49,"<p>Jake and Rosa assimilate to their new lives behind bars, but both are coping in very different ways. Jake bonds with his cellmate, Caleb, and is forced to join a prison gang led by notorious inmate Romero, in order to gain his protection. Meanwhile, in the women&apos;s prison, Rosa puts Holt and Terry to the test by having them complete outrageous favors for her. Back in the precinct, Amy and Charles are doing all they can to exonerate their colleagues.</p>",1,5,30,"2017-09-26","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/129/323021.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1223230/brooklyn-nine-nine-5x01-the-big-house-part-1"),
(1264155,"The Big House, Part 2",49,"<p>When the warden asks Jake to investigate Romero&apos;s drug smuggling operation, Jake and Caleb find themselves caught between the loyalty Jake has sworn to both of them. Meanwhile, Amy is offered a deal by a local mobster who claims he can prove that Hawkins is guilty, but Holt and the rest of the gang think they have a safer plan.</p>",2,5,30,"2017-10-03","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/130/325056.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1264155/brooklyn-nine-nine-5x02-the-big-house-part-2"),
(1264156,"Kicks",49,"<p>Now that he&apos;s officially back at the precinct and desperate to solve a real case, Jake finds a loophole to get out of his temporarily designated desk duty. Unfortunately, that loophole rests on his ability to pass an official evaluation performed by Holt. While Charles provides Jake with moral support, Terry and Amy help Rosa, who believes Pimento may be cheating on her.</p>",3,5,30,"2017-10-10","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/292/732278.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1264156/brooklyn-nine-nine-5x03-kicks"),
(1264157,"HalloVeen",49,"<p>The Nine-Nine embarks on its fifth annual Halloween Heist and, as usual, everybody has a plan and no one is safe. Relationships and friendships are tested as the title &quot;Amazing Human Slash Genius&quot; must be snagged by midnight, leaving everyone pitted against each other.</p>",4,5,30,"2017-10-17","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015953.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1264157/brooklyn-nine-nine-5x04-halloveen"),
(1329900,"Bad Beat",49,"<p>To track down the infamous arms dealer Dan &quot;Daniel&quot; Valdano, Jake and Terry go undercover at an illegal gambling club, but when Holt gets involved to coach the two in the art of poker, his addiction resurfaces. Meanwhile, Boyle buys a food truck that was formerly used in a brutal string of murders without telling his investor, Amy, and Hitchcock and Scully challenge Rosa to a &quot;Butt-lympics&quot;.</p>",5,5,30,"2017-11-07","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/134/335729.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1329900/brooklyn-nine-nine-5x05-bad-beat"),
(1335261,"The Venue",49,"<p>The always unwelcome Vulture pops back into Jake and Amy&apos;s lives, threatening to swoop in and take something important away from them. Meanwhile, Boyle and Rosa must track down &quot;Sergeant Peanut Butter,&quot; the kidnapped NYPD horse that Charles envies, and Holt challenges Terry to be less image-conscious.</p>",6,5,30,"2017-11-14","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015954.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1335261/brooklyn-nine-nine-5x06-the-venue"),
(1347685,"Two Turkeys",49,"<p>Jake and Amy attempt to get their parents to bond over Thanksgiving dinner, but their first holiday together as a family does not go well. Meanwhile, at the precinct, Holt and Kevin&apos;s special Thanksgiving pie is stolen from his office and Holt searches through the ranks for the possible culprit.</p>",7,5,30,"2017-11-21","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/136/340272.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1347685/brooklyn-nine-nine-5x07-two-turkeys"),
(1340986,"Return to Skyfire",49,"<p>When Terry&apos;s favorite author, DC Parlov, returns to the precinct because his latest manuscript was stolen, Terry and Jake convince Rosa to go undercover with them at a fantasy fiction convention to find the culprit. As drama ensues between Parlov and another writer, Terry admits that he&apos;s been writing a book of his own. Back at the precinct, Holt, Amy and Charles take a forensics course, but Charles&apos; big mouth gets him in trouble.</p>",8,5,30,"2017-11-28","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015955.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1340986/brooklyn-nine-nine-5x08-return-to-skyfire"),
(1357073,"99",49,"<p>While the entire precinct attends a funeral in LA, Holt learns that he is in the running to become Chief Commissioner of the NYPD - his dream job. But after missing their flight back to New York, Jake must devise a variety of ways to get Holt back in time for the interview. Forced to stay with some estranged members of the Boyle family, Amy tries to convince everyone that she can be laid back, Terry panics about losing his first-class flight and Charles uncovers some new information about Rosa&apos;s personal life.</p>",9,5,30,"2017-12-05","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015956.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1357073/brooklyn-nine-nine-5x09-99"),
(1360129,"Game Night",49,"<p>Rosa begs Jake to help her break some big news to her parents, but her plan is thrown off when they wrongly assume the two are dating. Gina returns to help the 99 get their internet access back from the Cyber Crimes division.</p>",10,5,30,"2017-12-12","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/138/346087.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1360129/brooklyn-nine-nine-5x10-game-night"),
(1360130,"The Favor",49,"<p>When Seamus Murphy returns to redeem the favor Holt owes him, the precinct searches for a loophole that will allow Holt to uphold his end of the bargain without breaking the law.</p>",11,5,30,"2017-12-12","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/138/346088.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1360130/brooklyn-nine-nine-5x11-the-favor"),
(1420087,"Safe House",49,"<p>After Seamus threatens Kevin, Holt devises an elaborate plan to hide him in a safe house, with Jake as his guard. Kevin is miserable as the 99 works overtime to find Seamus and take him down.</p>",12,5,30,"2018-03-18","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/406/1015957.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1420087/brooklyn-nine-nine-5x12-safe-house"),
(1420088,"The Negotiation",49,"<p>Jake is called upon to negotiate a hostage situation with a jewel thief, only to discover that the culprit seems to be a familiar face. Amy and Gina help Charles with the high demands of his new food truck, and Holt panics when a member of the Police Commissioner selection committee decides to interview Hitchcock about Holt.</p>",13,5,30,"2018-03-25","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/150/376546.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1420088/brooklyn-nine-nine-5x13-the-negotiation"),
