(2270891,"Lock and Key",269,"<p>A war veteran who fought in the trenches, Tommy Shelby has been a gangster, an entrepreneur, a captain of industry, a spy and ultimately a Member of Parliament. In the course of this odyssey, he has taken on numerous criminal organisations, business adversaries, foreign insurgents, and the British Establishment itself.</p><p>Now, in the 1930s, as the clouds of the coming storm gather, he faces the consequences of his experiences and his actions.</p>",6,6,80,"2022-04-03","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/401/1004177.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2270891/peaky-blinders-6x06-lock-and-key"),
