(67445,"Mission to the Unknown",766,"<p><i><b>Missing episode</b></i></p><p>On the planet Kembel, Space Security Service agent Marc Cory is investigating a recent sighting of a Dalek spaceship. His suspicion that the creatures may have established a base proves well-founded. He learns of a plot by the Daleks to invade and destroy the Solar System, but he is discovered and exterminated. The Daleks and their allies vow to conquer the universe, beginning with the planet Earth.</p>",5,3,25,"1965-10-09",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67445/doctor-who-3x05-mission-to-the-unknown"),
