(67486,"The Smugglers, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor discovers Polly and Ben aboard the TARDIS shortly before the ship arrives in 17th century Cornwall, where the local churchwarden gives the Doctor a cryptic message shortly before being murdered.</p>",1,4,25,"1966-09-10",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67486/doctor-who-4x01-the-smugglers-part-one"),
(67487,"The Smugglers, Part Two",766,"<p>Pike is convinced that the Doctor knows the location of Avery&apos;s treasure while Polly and Ben try to convince the locals they were not responsible for Longfoot&apos;s murder.</p>",2,4,25,"1966-09-17",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67487/doctor-who-4x02-the-smugglers-part-two"),
(67488,"The Smugglers, Part Three",766,"<p>Polly and Ben are placed in the custody of Blake, who reveals he also has his suspicions about the Squire, while the Doctor and Kewper are forced to team up to escape from Pike&apos;s ship.</p>",3,4,25,"1966-09-24",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67488/doctor-who-4x03-the-smugglers-part-three"),
(67489,"The Smugglers, Part Four",766,"<p>The Doctor and his friends are at the mercy of Cherub, who is now seeking Avery&apos;s treasure for himself, while Pike prepares to attack the village.</p>",4,4,25,"1966-10-01",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67489/doctor-who-4x04-the-smugglers-part-four"),
(67490,"The Tenth Planet, Part One",766,"<p>In December 1986, a new planet appears in the Solar System which turns out to be a long-lost twin of Earth&apos;s named Mondas. Its inhabitants are the Cybermen.</p>",5,4,25,"1966-10-08",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67490/doctor-who-4x05-the-tenth-planet-part-one"),
(67491,"The Tenth Planet, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor&apos;s warnings are ignored and the Cybermen take over the base, hampering the crew&apos;s efforts to help Zeus IV.</p>",6,4,25,"1966-10-15",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67491/doctor-who-4x06-the-tenth-planet-part-two"),
(67492,"The Tenth Planet, Part Three",766,"<p>With the Doctor out of action, it is up to Polly, Ben and Barclay to stop Cutler using the Z-Bomb and devastating half the world.</p>",7,4,25,"1966-10-22",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67492/doctor-who-4x07-the-tenth-planet-part-three"),
(67493,"The Tenth Planet, Part Four",766,"<p>The Cybermen take over the base again, apparently to stop the humans using the Z-Bomb, but then the Doctor realises they intend to use it themselves to destroy Earth.</p>",8,4,25,"1966-10-29",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67493/doctor-who-4x08-the-tenth-planet-part-four"),
(67494,"The Power of the Daleks, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor and his companions are brought to an Earth colony on the planet Vulcan.</p>",9,4,25,"1966-11-05","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/90/225956.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67494/doctor-who-4x09-the-power-of-the-daleks-part-one"),
(67495,"The Power of the Daleks, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor warns the scientist about the dire consequences of reactivating the dormant Dalek that he claims not to have discovered. The Doctor attempts to see the governor in an attempt to stop the secret experiments with the Dalek,.</p>",10,4,25,"1966-11-12","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/90/225962.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67495/doctor-who-4x10-the-power-of-the-daleks-part-two"),
(67496,"The Power of the Daleks, Part Three",766,"<p>Polly is taken prisoner by the rebels who are planning to use the Dalek to take control of the colony.</p>",11,4,25,"1966-11-19","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/90/225969.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67496/doctor-who-4x11-the-power-of-the-daleks-part-three"),
(67497,"The Power of the Daleks, Part Four",766,"<p>Scientist Lesterson discovers the Daleks plot to reproduce themselves and then seize control of the Colony.</p>",12,4,25,"1966-11-26","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/90/225970.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67497/doctor-who-4x12-the-power-of-the-daleks-part-four"),
(67498,"The Power of the Daleks, Part Five",766,"<p>The head of security for the Earth colony Vulcan, leads a rebellion; The Daleks prepare to make their final assault on the people of the colony.</p>",13,4,25,"1966-12-03","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/91/228083.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67498/doctor-who-4x13-the-power-of-the-daleks-part-five"),
(67499,"The Power of the Daleks, Part Six",766,"<p>The Daleks begin their attack while the battle rages between the loyalists and the rebels and it falls to the Doctor to make an attempt to stop the Daleks plot.</p>",14,4,25,"1966-12-10","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/91/228431.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67499/doctor-who-4x14-the-power-of-the-daleks-part-six"),
(67500,"The Highlanders, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor, Polly and Ben arrive in 1746, in the aftermath of the Battle of Culloden, and are captured by a group of Highlanders shortly before they themselves are captured by redcoats.</p>",15,4,25,"1966-12-17",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67500/doctor-who-4x15-the-highlanders-part-one"),
(67501,"The Highlanders, Part Two",766,"<p>Polly and Kirsty capture Lieutenant Ffinch to try and enlist his help while the Doctor tricks Gray in order to escape.</p>",16,4,25,"1966-12-24",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67501/doctor-who-4x16-the-highlanders-part-two"),
(67502,"The Highlanders, Part Three",766,"<p>With the Highlanders imprisoned aboard Trask&apos;s ship, the Doctor attempts to expose Grey&apos;s plan.</p>",17,4,25,"1966-12-31",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67502/doctor-who-4x17-the-highlanders-part-three"),
(67503,"The Highlanders, Part Four",766,"<p>Ben manages to join up with the Doctor, Polly and Kirsty and together they work to free the Highlanders from Trask&apos;s ship before Grey sells them into slavery.</p>",18,4,25,"1967-01-07",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67503/doctor-who-4x18-the-highlanders-part-four"),
(67504,"The Underwater Menace, Part One",766,"<p>The TARDIS materializes on a stretch of deserted beach. The Doctor and his companions are then captured and taken to the mysterious lost city of Atlantis.</p>",19,4,25,"1967-01-14","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/58/145505.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67504/doctor-who-4x19-the-underwater-menace-part-one"),
(67505,"The Underwater Menace, Part Two",766,"<p>While Ara tries to save Polly from being turned into a Fish Person and Ben and Jamie try to escape from the mines, the Doctor discovers the full extent of Zaroff&apos;s plans.</p>",20,4,25,"1967-01-21",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67505/doctor-who-4x20-the-underwater-menace-part-two"),
(67506,"The Underwater Menace, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor and Ramo are sentenced to be sacrificed to the goddess Amdo and must escape to put a stop to Zaroff&apos;s plan.</p>",21,4,25,"1967-01-28",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67506/doctor-who-4x21-the-underwater-menace-part-three"),
(67507,"The Underwater Menace, Part Four",766,"<p>With Zaroff&apos;s plan nearing completion, the Doctor and Ben realise the only way to save the world is to destroy Atlantis.</p>",22,4,25,"1967-02-04",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67507/doctor-who-4x22-the-underwater-menace-part-four"),
(67508,"The Moonbase, Part One",766,"<p>The TARDIS arrives on the Moon in the year 2070. When Jamie is injured, the other travellers are forced to seek the help of a moonbase afflicted with a space plague.</p>",23,4,25,"1967-02-11",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67508/doctor-who-4x23-the-moonbase-part-one"),
(67509,"The Moonbase, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor and his friends attempt to convince the Moonbase crew that the Cybermen are responsible for the disappearances and find a cure for the plague.</p>",24,4,25,"1967-02-18",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67509/doctor-who-4x24-the-moonbase-part-two"),
(67510,"The Moonbase, Part Three",766,"<p>The Cybermen take over the Moonbase and begin using the Gravitron to attack Earth but Polly, Ben and Jamie come up with a way to fight back.</p>",25,4,25,"1967-02-25",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67510/doctor-who-4x25-the-moonbase-part-three"),
(67511,"The Moonbase, Part Four",766,"<p>With the Cybermen preparing to launch a full attack, the Doctor and his friends must keep the Moonbase and the Gravitron out of their hands until help arrives from Earth.</p>",26,4,25,"1967-03-04",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67511/doctor-who-4x26-the-moonbase-part-four"),
(67512,"The Macra Terror, Part One",766,"<p>The TARDIS arrives at a holiday camp company with the crew worried by a prediction of giant crabs and the Doctor becomes interested in the apparent madman Medok&apos;s stories of creatures that roam the colony at night.</p>",27,4,25,"1967-03-11",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67512/doctor-who-4x27-the-macra-terror-part-one"),
(67513,"The Macra Terror, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor is unable to convince the colonists that the Macra exist and an attempt to brainwash his companions results in Ben betraying his friends.</p>",28,4,25,"1967-03-18",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67513/doctor-who-4x28-the-macra-terror-part-two"),
(67514,"The Macra Terror, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor, Polly and Jamie are sentenced to work in the pits and an escape attempt sees Ben&apos;s loyalties called into question again.</p>",29,4,25,"1967-03-25",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67514/doctor-who-4x29-the-macra-terror-part-three"),
(67515,"The Macra Terror, Part Four",766,"<p>The Doctor and Polly manage to save Jamie from the Macra and then try to show the Pilot who is really in charge of the colony.</p>",30,4,25,"1967-04-01",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67515/doctor-who-4x30-the-macra-terror-part-four"),
(67516,"The Faceless Ones, Part One",766,"<p>The TARDIS materialises on the runway of Gatwick Airport, where Polly witnesses a murder only to be kidnapped before she can report it.</p>",31,4,25,"1967-04-08",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67516/doctor-who-4x31-the-faceless-ones-part-one"),
(67517,"The Faceless Ones, Part Two",766,"<p>With Polly having apparently forgotten them, the Doctor, Ben and Jamie decide to carry out their own investigation of Chameleon Tours.</p>",32,4,25,"1967-04-15",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67517/doctor-who-4x32-the-faceless-ones-part-two"),
(67518,"The Faceless Ones, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Sam manage to convince Crossland to trust them and he persuades the Commandant to let them continue their investigation.</p>",33,4,25,"1967-04-22",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67518/doctor-who-4x33-the-faceless-ones-part-three"),
(67519,"The Faceless Ones, Part Four",766,"<p>When Spencer attempts to kill them, the Doctor, Jamie and Sam become convinced Chameleon Tours are hiding something and Sam decides to book a ticket on one of their flights.</p>",34,4,25,"1967-04-29",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67519/doctor-who-4x34-the-faceless-ones-part-four"),
(67520,"The Faceless Ones, Part Five",766,"<p>Jamie finds himself aboard the Chameleons&apos; satellite and meets their Director while the Doctor forces the Chameleon Meadows to tell him the aliens&apos; plans.</p>",35,4,25,"1967-05-06",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67520/doctor-who-4x35-the-faceless-ones-part-five"),
(67521,"The Faceless Ones, Part Six",766,"<p>The Doctor and Pinto are captured by the Chameleons but the Doctor manages to use their dependence on their human originals to create dissent in their ranks.</p>",36,4,25,"1967-05-13",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67521/doctor-who-4x36-the-faceless-ones-part-six"),
(67522,"The Evil of the Daleks, Part One",766,"<p>Trying to find the stolen TARDIS, the Doctor and Jamie are lured into a trap by the Doctor&apos;s old enemies the Daleks.</p>",37,4,25,"1967-05-20",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67522/doctor-who-4x37-the-evil-of-the-daleks-part-one");
