(67524,"The Evil of the Daleks, Part Three",766,"<p>As part of the Daleks&apos; experiment, the Doctor manipulates Jamie into attempting to rescue Victoria.</p>",39,4,25,"1967-06-03",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67524/doctor-who-4x39-the-evil-of-the-daleks-part-three"),
(67525,"The Evil of the Daleks, Part Four",766,"<p>Jamie and Kemel team up to try and find Victoria, while the Doctor and the Daleks continue to monitor their progress.</p>",40,4,25,"1967-06-10",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67525/doctor-who-4x40-the-evil-of-the-daleks-part-four"),
(67526,"The Evil of the Daleks, Part Five",766,"<p>With the experiment at an end, the Doctor begins to suspect the key to rescuing Jamie, Victoria and Kemel from the Daleks lies with Terrall.</p>",41,4,25,"1967-06-17",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67526/doctor-who-4x41-the-evil-of-the-daleks-part-five"),
