(67528,"The Evil of the Daleks, Part Seven",766,"<p>The Daleks are poised to spread the Dalek Factor throughout the history of Earth and begin by implanting the Doctor.</p>",43,4,25,"1967-07-01",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67528/doctor-who-4x43-the-evil-of-the-daleks-part-seven"),
(67529,"The Tomb of the Cybermen, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Victoria arrive on Telos, where an archaeological group are exploring the Tomb of the Cybermen. But are the Cybermen as dormant as they believe?</p>",1,5,25,"1967-09-02",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67529/doctor-who-5x01-the-tomb-of-the-cybermen-part-one"),
(67530,"The Tomb of the Cybermen, Part Two",766,"<p>The archaeologists learn they are stranded on Telos and Klieg suggests they use the opportunity to explore the Cybermen&apos;s tombs.</p>",2,5,25,"1967-09-09",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67530/doctor-who-5x02-the-tomb-of-the-cybermen-part-two"),
(67531,"The Tomb of the Cybermen, Part Three",766,"<p>The Cybermen have been revived and plan to convert the archeologists into their own kind, prompting Hopper to attempt a rescue.</p>",3,5,25,"1967-09-16",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67531/doctor-who-5x03-the-tomb-of-the-cybermen-part-three"),
(67532,"The Tomb of the Cybermen, Part Four",766,"<p>Klieg attempts to do a deal with the Cybercontroller while the Doctor tries to find a way to refreeze the Cybermen permanently.</p>",4,5,25,"1967-09-23",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67532/doctor-who-5x04-the-tomb-of-the-cybermen-part-four"),
(67533,"The Abominable Snowmen, Part One",766,"<p>When the TARDIS materialises in the Himalayas, the Doctor decides to pay a return visit to the nearby Det-Sen monastery only to be accused of murder.</p>",5,5,25,"1967-09-30",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67533/doctor-who-5x05-the-abominable-snowmen-part-one"),
(67534,"The Abominable Snowmen, Part Two",766,"<p>Jamie and Victoria make their way to the monastery shortly before it is attacked by the Yeti.</p>",6,5,25,"1967-10-07",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67534/doctor-who-5x06-the-abominable-snowmen-part-two"),
(67535,"The Abominable Snowmen, Part Three",766,"<p>While the Doctor and Jamie return to the TARDIS for equipment, the control sphere Jamie brought to the monastery is reactivated.</p>",7,5,25,"1967-10-14",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67535/doctor-who-5x07-the-abominable-snowmen-part-three"),
(67536,"The Abominable Snowmen, Part Four",766,"<p>The Yeti escapes from the monastery and Victoria and Thonmi are accused of assisting it, while the Doctor and Jamie endure a perilous journey back across the mountains.</p>",8,5,25,"1967-10-21",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67536/doctor-who-5x08-the-abominable-snowmen-part-four"),
(67537,"The Abominable Snowmen, Part Five",766,"<p>Victoria falls under the mental influence of Padmasambhva as the Yeti attack in order to drive the monks from the area.</p>",9,5,25,"1967-10-28",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67537/doctor-who-5x09-the-abominable-snowmen-part-five"),
(67538,"The Abominable Snowmen, Part Six",766,"<p>With the Great Intelligence on the verge of becoming corporeal, the Doctor challenges Padmasambhva to a mental battle in order to defeat it.</p>",10,5,25,"1967-11-04",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67538/doctor-who-5x10-the-abominable-snowmen-part-six"),
(67539,"The Ice Warriors, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Victoria are brought to a base which is attempting to halt the flow of the Second Ice Age.</p>",11,5,25,"1967-11-11",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67539/doctor-who-5x11-the-ice-warriors-part-one"),
(67540,"The Ice Warriors, Part Two",766,"<p>Varga revives and takes Victoria hostage as he works to revive his crew while the Doctor and Jamie find Penley stealing medical supplies.</p>",12,5,25,"1967-11-18",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67540/doctor-who-5x12-the-ice-warriors-part-two"),
(67541,"The Ice Warriors, Part Three",766,"<p>Jamie and Arden venture out to rescue Victoria only to find the rest of the Ice Warriors are now active.</p>",13,5,25,"1967-11-25",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67541/doctor-who-5x13-the-ice-warriors-part-three"),
(67542,"The Ice Warriors, Part Four",766,"<p>The Doctor leaves the base to try and find Jamie and Victoria while Storr tries to do a deal with the Ice Warriors.</p>",14,5,25,"1967-12-02",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67542/doctor-who-5x14-the-ice-warriors-part-four"),
(67543,"The Ice Warriors, Part Five",766,"<p>The Doctor and Victoria are both held prisoner by the Ice Warriors as Varga decides to take over Brittanicus.</p>",15,5,25,"1967-12-09",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67543/doctor-who-5x15-the-ice-warriors-part-five"),
(67544,"The Ice Warriors, Part Six",766,"<p>The Doctor and Victoria attempt to force the Ice Warriors to surrender control of the ioniser before the ice flow destroys them.</p>",16,5,25,"1967-12-16",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67544/doctor-who-5x16-the-ice-warriors-part-six"),
(67545,"The Enemy of the World, Part One",766,"<p>After the Doctor is attacked by a group of mysterious gunmen, he discovers he is the physical double of the famous scientist Salamander.</p>",17,5,25,"1967-12-23",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67545/doctor-who-5x17-the-enemy-of-the-world-part-one"),
(67546,"The Enemy of the World, Part Two",766,"<p>Jamie and Victoria agree to accompany Astrid to Hungary to observe Salamander&apos;s activities.</p>",18,5,25,"1967-12-30",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67546/doctor-who-5x18-the-enemy-of-the-world-part-two"),
(67547,"The Enemy of the World, Part Three",766,"<p>Jamie and Victoria become friends with Fariah, determined to discover the truth about Salamander. Astrid makes plans to rescue Denes, but not everything goes to plan.</p>",19,5,25,"1968-01-06",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67547/doctor-who-5x19-the-enemy-of-the-world-part-three"),
(67548,"The Enemy of the World, Part Four",766,"<p>Fariah brings the Doctor and Kent evidence of Salamander&apos;s activities but then they come under attack from Benik.</p>",20,5,25,"1968-01-13",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67548/doctor-who-5x20-the-enemy-of-the-world-part-four"),
(67549,"The Enemy of the World, Part Five",766,"<p>The Doctor persuades Bruce to help him infiltrate Salamander&apos;s research centre while Salamander takes drastic action to prevent Swann finding out the truth.</p>",21,5,25,"1968-01-20",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67549/doctor-who-5x21-the-enemy-of-the-world-part-five"),
(67550,"The Enemy of the World, Part Six",766,"<p>The Doctor discovers the true link between Salamander and Kent while Astrid tries to convince the shelter inhabitants they have been lied to.</p>",22,5,25,"1968-01-27",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67550/doctor-who-5x22-the-enemy-of-the-world-part-six"),
(67551,"The Web of Fear, Part One",766,"<p>The TARDIS becomes trapped in space before ending up in an underground station of a mysteriously deserted London.</p>",23,5,25,"1968-02-03",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67551/doctor-who-5x23-the-web-of-fear-part-one"),
(67552,"The Web of Fear, Part Two",766,"<p>Jamie and Victoria are reunited with Travers before Jamie joins the soldiers in attempting to find out what has happened to the Doctor.</p>",24,5,25,"1968-02-10",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67552/doctor-who-5x24-the-web-of-fear-part-two"),
(67553,"The Web of Fear, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor and Victoria are taken back to the Goodge Street base by Colonel Lethbridge-Stewart where the Doctor becomes convinced there is a traitor in their midst.</p>",25,5,25,"1968-02-17",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67553/doctor-who-5x25-the-web-of-fear-part-three"),
(67554,"The Web of Fear, Part Four",766,"<p>With Travers having been captured by the Yeti, the Doctor attempts to find a way to gain control of the robots while Lethbridge-Stewart tries to recover the TARDIS.</p>",26,5,25,"1968-02-24",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67554/doctor-who-5x26-the-web-of-fear-part-four"),
(67555,"The Web of Fear, Part Five",766,"<p>Victoria and Travers are held prisoner by the Great Intelligence, who is planning to drain the Doctor&apos;s mind.</p>",27,5,25,"1968-03-02",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67555/doctor-who-5x27-the-web-of-fear-part-five"),
(67556,"The Web of Fear, Part Six",766,"<p>The Doctor and his friends are held prisoner by the Intelligence and their only hope lies with Jamie, Arnold and a reprogrammed Yeti.</p>",28,5,25,"1968-03-09",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67556/doctor-who-5x28-the-web-of-fear-part-six"),
(67557,"Fury from the Deep, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Victoria are taken prisoner by the staff of a gas refinery, who have lost contact with their drilling rigs and experienced mysterious drops in pressure.</p>",29,5,25,"1968-03-16",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67557/doctor-who-5x29-fury-from-the-deep-part-one"),
(67558,"Fury from the Deep, Part Two",766,"<p>Harris asks for the Doctor&apos;s help with Maggie while Van Lutyens and the Chief Engineer attempt to determine what is blocking the impeller.</p>",30,5,25,"1968-03-23",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67558/doctor-who-5x30-fury-from-the-deep-part-two"),
(67559,"Fury from the Deep, Part Three",766,"<p>While the Doctor begins his investigation into the weed creatures, Robson is attacked by one at the refinery.</p>",31,5,25,"1968-03-30",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67559/doctor-who-5x31-fury-from-the-deep-part-three"),
(67560,"Fury from the Deep, Part Four",766,"<p>Van Lutyens&apos; investigation of the base of the impeller places the Doctor and Jamie in danger from the Weed Creature.</p>",32,5,25,"1968-04-06",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67560/doctor-who-5x32-fury-from-the-deep-part-four"),
(67561,"Fury from the Deep, Part Five",766,"<p>With the Weed Creature poised to burst out of the pipeline and attack the base, an encounter with Oak and Quill gives the Doctor a vital clue about its weakness.</p>",33,5,25,"1968-04-13",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67561/doctor-who-5x33-fury-from-the-deep-part-five"),
(67562,"Fury from the Deep, Part Six",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jamie rescue Victoria from Robson and realise they can destroy the Weed Creature with sound waves.</p>",34,5,25,"1968-04-20",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67562/doctor-who-5x34-fury-from-the-deep-part-six"),
(67563,"The Wheel in Space, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jamie arrive on a mysterious spacecraft whose only occupant is a dangerous Servo Robot.</p>",35,5,25,"1968-04-27",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67563/doctor-who-5x35-the-wheel-in-space-part-one"),
(67564,"The Wheel in Space, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jamie are brought aboard the Wheel where Jamie is horrified to learn the crew plan to destroy the Silver Carrier with the TARDIS on board.</p>",36,5,25,"1968-05-04",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67564/doctor-who-5x36-the-wheel-in-space-part-two"),
(67565,"The Wheel in Space, Part Three",766,"<p>Jamie sabotages the Wheel&apos;s x-ray laser, unknowingly giving the Cybermen an opportunity to reach the Wheel.</p>",37,5,25,"1968-05-11",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67565/doctor-who-5x37-the-wheel-in-space-part-three"),
(67566,"The Wheel in Space, Part Four",766,"<p>The Cybermen instruct their human slaves to smuggle them onto the Wheel while the Doctor attempts to convince Bennett of the threat they pose.</p>",38,5,25,"1968-05-18",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67566/doctor-who-5x38-the-wheel-in-space-part-four"),
(67567,"The Wheel in Space, Part Five",766,"<p>The Cybermen gain control of more members of the Wheel crew and the Doctor realises the only way to stop them is for Jamie and Zoe to make a dangerous space walk.</p>",39,5,25,"1968-05-25",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67567/doctor-who-5x39-the-wheel-in-space-part-five"),
(67568,"The Wheel in Space, Part Six",766,"<p>Jamie and Zoe attempt to recover the time vector generator while the Cybermen realise the Doctor is on the Wheel and make him their prime target.</p>",40,5,25,"1968-06-01",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67568/doctor-who-5x40-the-wheel-in-space-part-six"),
(67569,"The Dominators, Part One",766,"<p>The TARDIS arrives on the planet Dulkis where the Doctor, Zoe and Jamie decide to have a quiet holiday. Only to find the Evil Dominators and their robotic slaves, The Quarks have arrived on a radioactive island, where they plan to detonate a bomb in the planet&apos;s core, which will turn the entire planet as source of radioactive fuel for their invasion fleet.</p>",1,6,25,"1968-08-10","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/286/716598.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67569/doctor-who-6x01-the-dominators-part-one"),
(67570,"The Dominators, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jamie are captured by the Dominators, who subject them to an intelligence test, while Zoe and Cully attempt to convince the Dulcian council of the threat.</p>",2,6,25,"1968-08-17",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67570/doctor-who-6x02-the-dominators-part-two"),
(67571,"The Dominators, Part Three",766,"<p>Zoe and Cully are captured by the Dominators and put to work alongside the survey team while the Doctor and Jamie decide to return to the island to help.</p>",3,6,25,"1968-08-24","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281604.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67571/doctor-who-6x03-the-dominators-part-three"),
(67572,"The Dominators, Part Four",766,"<p>The Doctor and Zoe are interrogated by Rago, who is planning to present his terms to the Dulcian council, while Jamie and Cully try to find a way to strike back against the Quarks.</p>",4,6,25,"1968-08-31","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281605.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67572/doctor-who-6x04-the-dominators-part-four"),
(67573,"The Dominators, Part Five",766,"<p>Jamie and Cully manage to rescue the Doctor&apos;s party and together they try to find a way to stop the Dominators before they destroy the entire planet.</p>",5,6,25,"1968-09-07","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281609.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67573/doctor-who-6x05-the-dominators-part-five"),
(67574,"The Mind Robber, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor activates an emergency unit on board theTARDIS to escape destruction by a volcanic eruption. Unfortunately, it moves them out of normal space and time to a deadly world where fantasy rules. The travellers find themselves lured out of the ship into a ghostly white void.</p>",6,6,25,"1968-09-14","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281610.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67574/doctor-who-6x06-the-mind-robber-part-one"),
(67575,"The Mind Robber, Part Two",766,"<p>With the TARDIS destroyed, the Doctor, Jamie and Zoe find themselves in a strange forest patrolled by mysterious soldiers.</p>",7,6,25,"1968-09-21","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281611.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67575/doctor-who-6x07-the-mind-robber-part-two"),
(67576,"The Mind Robber, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor realises that the travelers are trapped in a world where fiction is real and where creatures are a threat if people believe in them.</p>",8,6,25,"1968-09-28","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281612.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67576/doctor-who-6x08-the-mind-robber-part-three"),
(67577,"The Mind Robber, Part Four",766,"<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Zoe reach the citadel at the centre of the land, where they finally encounter the Master of the Land of Fiction.</p>",9,6,25,"1968-10-05","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281613.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67577/doctor-who-6x09-the-mind-robber-part-four"),
(67578,"The Mind Robber, Part Five",766,"<p>With Jamie and Zoe having been turned into fiction, the Doctor must find a way to save them without suffering the same fate or becoming part of the Master Brain.</p>",10,6,25,"1968-10-12","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281615.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67578/doctor-who-6x10-the-mind-robber-part-five"),
(67579,"The Invasion, Part One",766,"<p>The TARDIS lands in London where the Doctor, Jamie and Zoe agree to help find Isobel Watkins&apos; missing uncle.Searching for Professor Watkins at his last place of work,a multinational electronics supplier, hemeets the company&apos;s managing director. He&apos;s not what he seems - and possesses alien technology in his office.</p>",11,6,25,"1968-11-02","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281623.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67579/doctor-who-6x11-the-invasion-part-one"),
(67580,"The Invasion, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jamie are taken prisoner by their mysterious observers and have a reunion with an old friend while Zoe and Isobel carry out their own investigation of IE.</p>",12,6,25,"1968-11-09","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281627.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67580/doctor-who-6x12-the-invasion-part-two"),
(67581,"The Invasion, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jamie return to the IE factory in search of Zoe and Isobel, where they meet with Professor Watkins and fall foul of Vaughn.</p>",13,6,25,"1968-11-16","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281629.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67581/doctor-who-6x13-the-invasion-part-three"),
(67582,"The Invasion, Part Four",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jamie enlist the help of UNIT to rescue Zoe and Isobel before trying to find out what Vaughn is really up to.</p>",14,6,25,"1968-11-23","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281649.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67582/doctor-who-6x14-the-invasion-part-four"),
(67583,"The Invasion, Part Five",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jamie tell the Brigadier about the Cybermen but with Rutledge under Vaughn&apos;s control he is powerless to act.</p>",15,6,25,"1968-11-30","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281784.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67583/doctor-who-6x15-the-invasion-part-five"),
(67584,"The Invasion, Part Six",766,"<p>Captain Turner manages to rescue Jamie and the others, while the Doctor begins working on a way to protect everyone from the Cybermen&apos;s hypno-sound signal.</p>",16,6,25,"1968-12-07","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281794.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67584/doctor-who-6x16-the-invasion-part-six"),
(67585,"The Invasion, Part Seven",766,"<p>With the entire world unconscious apart from the Doctor and his friends, the Cybermen are poised to invade and only Zoe, the Brigadier and a missile crew can stop them.</p>",17,6,25,"1968-12-14","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281796.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67585/doctor-who-6x17-the-invasion-part-seven"),
(67586,"The Invasion, Part Eight",766,"<p>The Cybermen have launched their deadly megatron bomb which will destroy all life on Earth unless the Doctor can deactivate the homing signal.</p>",18,6,25,"1968-12-21","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281812.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67586/doctor-who-6x18-the-invasion-part-eight"),
(67587,"The Krotons, Part One",766,"<p>The TARDIS lands on the planet of the Gonds, a primitive and enslaved people. Every year, two of the finest Gond students are sent to be &apos;companions&apos; of the mysterious and unseen Krotons. But the Doctor reveals that only death awaits them.</p>",19,6,25,"1968-12-28","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281813.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67587/doctor-who-6x19-the-krotons-part-one"),
(67588,"The Krotons, Part Two",766,"<p>Zoe is selected as a companion for the Krotons and the Doctor insists on joining her.</p>",20,6,25,"1969-01-04","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281814.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67588/doctor-who-6x20-the-krotons-part-two"),
(67589,"The Krotons, Part Three",766,"<p>Jamie is held prisoner by the Krotons who intend to recapture the Doctor and Zoe for their mental energy.</p>",21,6,25,"1969-01-11","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281816.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67589/doctor-who-6x21-the-krotons-part-three"),
(67590,"The Krotons, Part Four",766,"<p>Selris succeeds in drawing the Krotons out of the Dynatrope but Eelek agrees to hand the Doctor and Zoe over to them in return for their leaving the planet.</p>",22,6,25,"1969-01-18","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281828.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67590/doctor-who-6x22-the-krotons-part-four"),
(67591,"The Seeds of Death, Part One",766,"<p>21st century Earth is entirely dependent on the T-Mat transport system but the control centre on the moon has stopped functioning. Meanwhile, the Doctor, Jamie and Zoe meet the one man who can solve the crisis.</p>",23,6,25,"1969-01-25","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281829.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67591/doctor-who-6x23-the-seeds-of-death-part-one"),
(67592,"The Seeds of Death, Part Two",766,"<p>Eldred agrees to supply a rocket for travel to the moon and the Doctor, Jamie and Zoe volunteer to crew it.</p>",24,6,25,"1969-02-01","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281830.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67592/doctor-who-6x24-the-seeds-of-death-part-two"),
(67593,"The Seeds of Death, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Zoe make it to the moon and join forces with Phipps but the Ice Warriors have gained control of T-mat.</p>",25,6,25,"1969-02-08","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281831.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67593/doctor-who-6x25-the-seeds-of-death-part-three"),
(67594,"The Seeds of Death, Part Four",766,"<p>The Ice Warriors&apos; seed pods beginning materialising all over the globe while Slaar decides to kill the Doctor by T-matting him into space.</p>",26,6,25,"1969-02-15","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281832.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67594/doctor-who-6x26-the-seeds-of-death-part-four"),
(67595,"The Seeds of Death, Part Five",766,"<p>The Doctor and his allies manage to return to Earth via T-mat only to find the Ice Warrior has attacked the weather control station.</p>",27,6,25,"1969-02-22","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281929.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67595/doctor-who-6x27-the-seeds-of-death-part-five"),
(67596,"The Seeds of Death, Part Six",766,"<p>The Doctor manages to create a rain storm to destroy the Martian fungus before trying to find a way to stop the Ice Warriors&apos; invasion fleet.</p>",28,6,25,"1969-03-01","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281935.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67596/doctor-who-6x28-the-seeds-of-death-part-six"),
(67597,"The Space Pirates, Part One",766,"<p>Space beacons are being destroyed by pirates, who are salvaging the argonite metal. When the Doctor, Jamie and Zoe arrive on one of the beacons, they are mistaken for pirates.</p>",29,6,25,"1969-03-08",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67597/doctor-who-6x29-the-space-pirates-part-one"),
(67598,"The Space Pirates, Part Two",766,"<p>With the Doctor, Jamie and Zoe trapped on a beacon segment, Hermack becomes suspicious of the unruly prospector Milo Clancey.</p>",30,6,25,"1969-03-15","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/112/281936.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67598/doctor-who-6x30-the-space-pirates-part-two"),
(67599,"The Space Pirates, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor, Jamie and Zoe flee from the Space Corps with Clancey, who decides to seek refuge on Ta.</p>",31,6,25,"1969-03-22",null,"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/67599/doctor-who-6x31-the-space-pirates-part-three"),
