(315813,"Day of the Daleks, Part One",766,"<p>When someone tries to assassinate diplomat Sir Reginald Styles, UNIT investigate the possibility his attacker came from the future.</p>",1,9,25,"1972-01-01","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/167552.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/315813/doctor-who-9x01-day-of-the-daleks-part-one"),
(315814,"Day of the Daleks, Part Two",766,"<p>Jo uses the guerrillas&apos; time machine to travel to the 22nd century where the Controller tricks her into telling the Daleks where she&apos;s come from.</p>",2,9,25,"1972-01-08","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/167594.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/315814/doctor-who-9x02-day-of-the-daleks-part-two"),
(315815,"Day of the Daleks, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor forces the guerrillas to take him to the 22nd century where he is soon captured by the Controller.</p>",3,9,25,"1972-01-15","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/167599.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/315815/doctor-who-9x03-day-of-the-daleks-part-three"),
(315816,"Day of the Daleks, Part Four",766,"<p>The guerrillas infiltrate the Daleks&apos; base to rescue the Doctor and Jo and ask them to return to their own time and alter history before the 20th century is plunged into a Third World War.</p>",4,9,25,"1972-01-22","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/167609.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/315816/doctor-who-9x04-day-of-the-daleks-part-four"),
(315817,"The Curse of Peladon, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jo arrive on the medieval planet Peladon, where the Doctor is mistaken for the Earth Delegate of the Galactic Federation and Jo is mistaken for a princess. Where the Doctor uncovers a conspiracy, as he exposes the evil scheme of the high-priest Hepesh who bids to prevent King Peladon from joining the galactic Federation.</p>",5,9,25,"1972-01-29","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/167617.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/315817/doctor-who-9x05-the-curse-of-peladon-part-one"),
(315818,"The Curse of Peladon, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor is convinced the Ice Warriors are trying to sabotage the conference but his attempts to prove it see him accused of sacrilege.</p>",6,9,25,"1972-02-05","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/167630.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/315818/doctor-who-9x06-the-curse-of-peladon-part-two"),
(315837,"The Curse of Peladon, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor is sentenced to fight Grun to the death and his attempt to escape leads to an encounter with Aggedor.</p>",7,9,25,"1972-02-12","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/167641.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/315837/doctor-who-9x07-the-curse-of-peladon-part-three"),
(315859,"The Curse of Peladon, Part Four",766,"<p>Hepesh&apos;s plan has been exposed but he is still determined to prevent Peladon joining the Galactic Federation by leading a rebellion against the King.</p>",8,9,25,"1972-02-19","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/67/167654.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/315859/doctor-who-9x08-the-curse-of-peladon-part-four"),
(315883,"The Sea Devils, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jo visit the Master at his island prison where the Doctor becomes curious about a number of ships sinking in the area.</p>",9,9,25,"1972-02-26","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/84/212317.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/315883/doctor-who-9x09-the-sea-devils-part-one"),
(315904,"The Sea Devils, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jo are trapped on the fort by a Sea Devil while the Master convinces Trenchard to help him steal some electronic components.</p>",10,9,25,"1972-03-04","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/84/212446.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/315904/doctor-who-9x10-the-sea-devils-part-two"),
(316035,"The Sea Devils, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor is held prisoner by Trenchard while the Master attempts to contact the Sea Devils.</p>",11,9,25,"1972-03-11","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/85/212552.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316035/doctor-who-9x11-the-sea-devils-part-three"),
(316036,"The Sea Devils, Part Four",766,"<p>The Sea Devils attack the island prison and rescue the Master, prompting the Doctor to venture underwater to try and contact them.</p>",12,9,25,"1972-03-18","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/85/212556.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316036/doctor-who-9x12-the-sea-devils-part-four"),
(316037,"The Sea Devils, Part Five",766,"<p>The Doctor is taken to the Sea Devils&apos; underwater colony where he tries to make peace with the creatures, only for the navy to attack the base.</p>",13,9,25,"1972-03-25","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/85/212557.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316037/doctor-who-9x13-the-sea-devils-part-five"),
(316038,"The Sea Devils, Part Six",766,"<p>The Sea Devils take over the naval base and the Doctor is forced to help the Master find a way to revive their colony.</p>",14,9,25,"1972-04-01","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/85/212558.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316038/doctor-who-9x14-the-sea-devils-part-six"),
(316041,"The Mutants, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jo arrive on the planet Solos, on a assignment by the Time Lords. Where the Doctor and Jo learn that the native Solonians are mutating into ant-like mutant creatures and they uncover a conspiracy, where the evil Marshal of the Earth Empire plots to rule Solos for himself and plans to convert Solos atmosphere, since the planet&apos;s atmosphere is poisonous, so the planet can be colonized by the humans and he plans to wipe out all the mutated Solonians, who are evolving into a advanced super race.</p>",15,9,25,"1972-04-08","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/88/222435.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316041/doctor-who-9x15-the-mutants-part-one"),
(316042,"The Mutants, Part Two",766,"<p>Ky transports himself and Jo down to Solos and the Marshal only agrees to help her if the Doctor assists Professor Jaeger in altering Solos&apos; atmosphere.</p>",16,9,25,"1972-04-15","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/88/222436.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316042/doctor-who-9x16-the-mutants-part-two"),
(316044,"The Mutants, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor and Varan travel down to Solos to search for Jo and Ky but the Marshal orders his men to pursue them.</p>",17,9,25,"1972-04-22","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/88/222473.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316044/doctor-who-9x17-the-mutants-part-three"),
(316045,"The Mutants, Part Four",766,"<p>The Doctor and his friends are led to safety by Professor Sondergaard, who tries to help the Doctor translate the tablets.</p>",18,9,25,"1972-04-29","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/88/222475.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316045/doctor-who-9x18-the-mutants-part-four"),
(316053,"The Mutants, Part Five",766,"<p>The Marshal&apos;s premature use of Jaeger&apos;s experiment is threatening to destroy Solos&apos; atmosphere and the Doctor returns to Skybase to try and correct the damage.</p>",19,9,25,"1972-05-06","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/88/222476.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316053/doctor-who-9x19-the-mutants-part-five"),
(316054,"The Mutants, Part Six",766,"<p>The Doctor is forced to help the Marshal cover up his actions with the Investigator but Jo and the others attempt to escape to expose him.</p>",20,9,25,"1972-05-13","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/88/222478.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316054/doctor-who-9x20-the-mutants-part-six"),
(316055,"The Time Monster, Part One",766,"<p>UNIT are invited to observe a demonstration of the new TOMTIT machine, unaware its creator, Professor Thascales, is actually the Master.</p>",21,9,25,"1972-05-20","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285356.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316055/doctor-who-9x21-the-time-monster-part-one"),
(316056,"The Time Monster, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor realises the Master is trying to harness the power of Kronos, last of the Chronovores, but is unaware Percival is harbouring him at the institute.</p>",22,9,25,"1972-05-27","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285357.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316056/doctor-who-9x22-the-time-monster-part-two"),
(316057,"The Time Monster, Part Three",766,"<p>The Master enlists the help of Krasis to control Kronos while Yates tries to bring the TARDIS to the institute only to come under attack from dangers from the past.</p>",23,9,25,"1972-06-03","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285358.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316057/doctor-who-9x23-the-time-monster-part-three"),
(316060,"The Time Monster, Part Four",766,"<p>The Master prepares to travel back to Atlantis but the Doctor links his TARDIS to the Master&apos;s to try and stop him.</p>",24,9,25,"1972-06-10","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285360.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316060/doctor-who-9x24-the-time-monster-part-four"),
(316061,"The Time Monster, Part Five",766,"<p>Both TARDISes reach Atlantis, where the Doctor befriends King Dalios while the Master enlists the help of Queen Galleia to try and obtain the crystal of Kronos.</p>",25,9,25,"1972-06-17","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285361.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316061/doctor-who-9x25-the-time-monster-part-five"),
(316062,"The Time Monster, Part Six",766,"<p>The Doctor enters the labyrinth to try and protect Jo from the minotaur but the Master has seized control of Atlantis and prepares to summon Kronos again.</p>",26,9,25,"1972-06-24","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285362.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316062/doctor-who-9x26-the-time-monster-part-six"),
(316064,"The Three Doctors, Part One",766,"<p>The 10th Anniversary Serial has three incarnations of the Doctor meeting up to face the evil Omega in a universe of antimatter.</p>",1,10,25,"1972-12-30","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285364.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316064/doctor-who-10x01-the-three-doctors-part-one"),
(316065,"The Three Doctors, Part Two",766,"<p>The third Doctor and Jo find themselves on an artificial world inside the black hole while the second Doctor tries to find a way to control the organism.</p>",2,10,25,"1973-01-06","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285365.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316065/doctor-who-10x02-the-three-doctors-part-two"),
(316066,"The Three Doctors, Part Three",766,"<p>The Time Lord Omega reveals himself to the third Doctor along with plans for vengeance against his own kind.</p>",3,10,25,"1973-01-13","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285373.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316066/doctor-who-10x03-the-three-doctors-part-three"),
(316067,"The Three Doctors, Part Four",766,"<p>Omega reveals the purpose behind bringing the Doctor to his antimatter world, but the Doctor(s) discover a startling fact about Omega that he didn&apos;t know himself and eventually strike a bargain.</p>",4,10,25,"1973-01-20","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285383.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316067/doctor-who-10x04-the-three-doctors-part-four"),
(316068,"Carnival of Monsters, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor attempts to test his new dematerialisation circuit by taking Jo to Metebelis Three but instead the TARDIS arrives in the hold of a 1920s cargo ship.</p>",5,10,25,"1973-01-27","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285389.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316068/doctor-who-10x05-carnival-of-monsters-part-one"),
(316069,"Carnival of Monsters, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jo attempt to find a way out of the Scope but, when Vorg attempts to entertain the Minorans, the crew of the Bernice suddenly become a lot more dangerous.</p>",6,10,25,"1973-02-03","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285391.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316069/doctor-who-10x06-carnival-of-monsters-part-two"),
(316070,"Carnival of Monsters, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jo return to the Bernice to try and aid their escape but find themselves pursued by the Drashigs.</p>",7,10,25,"1973-02-10","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285392.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316070/doctor-who-10x07-carnival-of-monsters-part-three"),
(316071,"Carnival of Monsters, Part Four",766,"<p>The Doctor escapes from the Scope and joins forces with Vorg to try and save its inhabitants but Kalik is still determined to use the Drashigs to start a rebellion.</p>",8,10,25,"1973-02-17","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285404.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316071/doctor-who-10x08-carnival-of-monsters-part-four"),
(316072,"Frontier in Space, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jo discover The Master and the Ogrons are the masterminds behind the Galactic war between the Earth Federation and the Reptillian Draconian Empire and the Master has framed The Doctor and Jo as spies working for the Draconians. Only to discover The Master is also working with the Doctor&apos;s greatest enemies, The Daleks, who are also behind the galactic war.</p>",9,10,25,"1973-02-24","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285414.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316072/doctor-who-10x09-frontier-in-space-part-one"),
(316073,"Frontier in Space, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jo are taken to Earth, where both humans and Draconians believe them to be a spy for the other side.</p>",10,10,25,"1973-03-03","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285426.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316073/doctor-who-10x10-frontier-in-space-part-two"),
(316074,"Frontier in Space, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor is sentenced to life imprisonment at a lunar penal colony while Jo encounters an old enemy.</p>",11,10,25,"1973-03-10","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285428.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316074/doctor-who-10x11-frontier-in-space-part-three"),
(316075,"Frontier in Space, Part Four",766,"<p>The Master rescues the Doctor from the lunar penal colony, aiming to take him and Jo to the Ogrons&apos; planet, and the Doctor&apos;s attempt to escape leaves him stranded in space.</p>",12,10,25,"1973-03-17","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285803.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316075/doctor-who-10x12-frontier-in-space-part-four"),
(316076,"Frontier in Space, Part Five",766,"<p>The Doctor, Jo and the Master are taken to Draconia, where the Doctor tries to convince the Draconians of the truth. But then the Ogrons attack.</p>",13,10,25,"1973-03-24","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285804.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316076/doctor-who-10x13-frontier-in-space-part-five"),
(316077,"Frontier in Space, Part Six",766,"<p>The Doctor, Williams and the Draconian Prince head to the Ogrons&apos; planet to find evidence of the Master&apos;s actions but the Master tricks Jo into leading them into a trap.</p>",14,10,25,"1973-03-31","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285805.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316077/doctor-who-10x14-frontier-in-space-part-six"),
(316078,"Planet of the Daleks, Part One",766,"<p>The TARDIS lands on the jungle planet Spiridon, where the Doctor has fallen into a coma, where The Doctor has requested the Time Lords to pilot the TARDIS, so he and Jo can follow the Daleks to their base. Where Jo learns the Dalek&apos;s base has been located on Spiridon where the Daleks are attempting to discover the secrets of Invisibilty and create a bacterial virus in their goal of universal conquest. Where The Doctor, recovered from his coma and Jo are joined by a task-force of Thals and a native Spiridon named Wester, Where they not only set out to stop The Daleks evil plot, they also discover a army of 12,000 Daleks are in suspended animation and are waiting to be revived to begin their universal conquest and claim themselves as the supreme rulers of the galaxy.</p>",15,10,25,"1973-04-07","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285806.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316078/doctor-who-10x15-planet-of-the-daleks-part-one"),
(316079,"Planet of the Daleks, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor is captured by the Daleks, while Jo is rescued by a friendly Spridon named Wester.</p>",16,10,25,"1973-04-14","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285807.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316079/doctor-who-10x16-planet-of-the-daleks-part-two"),
(316080,"Planet of the Daleks, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor and Codal escape from their cell and meet up with the Thal commandos who are trying to get into the Dalek base.</p>",17,10,25,"1973-04-21","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285809.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316080/doctor-who-10x17-planet-of-the-daleks-part-three"),
(316081,"Planet of the Daleks, Part Four",766,"<p>The Doctor and his friends escape from the Dalek base, prompting the Daleks to devise a plan to wipe them out.</p>",18,10,25,"1973-04-28","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285810.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316081/doctor-who-10x18-planet-of-the-daleks-part-four"),
(316082,"Planet of the Daleks, Part Five",766,"<p>The Doctor and his friends ambush two Daleks as part of their planet to get back into the city but the Daleks are on the verge of unleashing their virus.</p>",19,10,25,"1973-05-05","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285811.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316082/doctor-who-10x19-planet-of-the-daleks-part-five"),
(316083,"Planet of the Daleks, Part Six",766,"<p>The Doctor and his friends prepare to refreeze the Dalek army but the Dalek Supreme has arrived on the planet determined to destroy them all.</p>",20,10,25,"1973-05-12","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285812.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316083/doctor-who-10x20-planet-of-the-daleks-part-six"),
(316084,"The Green Death, Part One",766,"<p>While the Doctor plans a holiday to Metebelis Three, Jo and the Brigadier are intrigued by a mysterious death at a coal mine in Llanfairfach, which is being blamed on local company Global Chemicals.</p>",21,10,25,"1973-05-19","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285813.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316084/doctor-who-10x21-the-green-death-part-one"),
(316085,"The Green Death, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor and the Brigadier attempt to rescue Jo and Bert from the mine but Global Chemicals prove distinctly uncooperative.</p>",22,10,25,"1973-05-26","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285818.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316085/doctor-who-10x22-the-green-death-part-two"),
(316086,"The Green Death, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor and Jo manage to escape from the mine with a maggot egg but Stevens is determined to stop them analysing it.</p>",23,10,25,"1973-06-02","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285828.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316086/doctor-who-10x23-the-green-death-part-three"),
(316087,"The Green Death, Part Four",766,"<p>The Brigadier calls in a full UNIT force to deal with the giant maggots while the Doctor infiltrates Global Chemicals to find out what is really going on.</p>",24,10,25,"1973-06-09","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285833.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316087/doctor-who-10x24-the-green-death-part-four"),
(316089,"The Green Death, Part Five",766,"<p>The Doctor manages to escape from BOSS with help from Yates and discovers Cliff has been infected by a giant maggot.</p>",25,10,25,"1973-06-16","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285837.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316089/doctor-who-10x25-the-green-death-part-five"),
(316090,"The Green Death, Part Six",766,"<p>The Doctor attempts to destroy the giant maggots and cure Cliff but the real threat is BOSS, who is poised to take over all the world&apos;s computers.</p>",26,10,25,"1973-06-23","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285860.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/316090/doctor-who-10x26-the-green-death-part-six"),
(323127,"The Time Warrior, Part One",766,"<p>The Brigadier asks the Doctor to investigate the disappearance of several scientists, only for him to find they have been abducted back in time.</p>",1,11,25,"1973-12-15","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285861.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323127/doctor-who-11x01-the-time-warrior-part-one"),
(323129,"The Time Warrior, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor tracks the missing scientists to Irongron&apos;s castle, where Linx is using them to repair his spaceship and construct advanced weapons for Irongron.</p>",2,11,25,"1973-12-22","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285863.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323129/doctor-who-11x02-the-time-warrior-part-two"),
(323130,"The Time Warrior, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor escapes the castle with Sarah and Hal and must persuade Sir Edward to trust him before Irongron launches an attack on them.</p>",3,11,25,"1973-12-29","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285868.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323130/doctor-who-11x03-the-time-warrior-part-three"),
(323131,"The Time Warrior, Part Four",766,"<p>The Doctor attempts to return the scientists to their own time, before Linx tries to use his spaceship and destroys the entire castle.</p>",4,11,25,"1974-01-05","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285870.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323131/doctor-who-11x04-the-time-warrior-part-four"),
(323132,"Invasion of the Dinosaurs, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor and Sarah return to London in the present day only to find the city strangely deserted, while nearby UNIT are dealing with a series of monster appearances.</p>",5,11,25,"1974-01-12","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285884.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323132/doctor-who-11x05-invasion-of-the-dinosaurs-part-one"),
(323134,"Invasion of the Dinosaurs, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor and Sarah returns to present-day Earth, where they find London has been evacuated, and Dinosaurs are on the loose and they are mistaken for looters. Assisting U.N.I.T in the emergency, The Doctor and Sarah discovers corrupt politician Sir Charles Grover MP, renegade scientists Butler and Professor Whitaker and military officer General Finch are using a time machine to bring the dinosaurs from the past to the present as part of they scheme to bring the human race back to a &quot;Golden Age&quot; before the world was polluted.</p>",6,11,25,"1974-01-19","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285890.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323134/doctor-who-11x06-invasion-of-the-dinosaurs-part-two"),
(323135,"Invasion of the Dinosaurs, Part Three",766,"<p>Yates sabotages the Doctor&apos;s equipment to stop him finding the location of Whitaker&apos;s base but then the tyrannosaur escapes, placing Sarah in danger.</p>",7,11,25,"1974-01-26","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285892.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323135/doctor-who-11x07-invasion-of-the-dinosaurs-part-three"),
(323137,"Invasion of the Dinosaurs, Part Four",766,"<p>Sarah attempts to find a way off the spaceship while the Doctor tries to track down the source of the time displacements.</p>",8,11,25,"1974-02-02","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285893.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323137/doctor-who-11x08-invasion-of-the-dinosaurs-part-four");
