(323139,"Invasion of the Dinosaurs, Part Five",766,"<p>The Doctor has been framed as the monster maker by Finch and is on the run from the army, while Sarah attempts to alert UNIT to what Grover is up to.</p>",9,11,25,"1974-02-09","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285894.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323139/doctor-who-11x09-invasion-of-the-dinosaurs-part-five"),
(323140,"Invasion of the Dinosaurs, Part Six",766,"<p>The Doctor is rescued from Finch by the Brigadier and Benton and tries to persuade them to stop Grover before millions of people are erased from history.</p>",10,11,25,"1974-02-16","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285895.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323140/doctor-who-11x10-invasion-of-the-dinosaurs-part-six"),
(323141,"Death to the Daleks, Part One",766,"<p>As the TARDIS heads to the paradise planet Florana where the Doctor and Sarah go for a holiday, the TARDIS goes off-course and arrives on the barren planet Exxilon, where the TARDIS is loosing power. The Doctor and Sarah finds a group of humans and Daleks are searching for Parrinium, a mineral which is the only antidote to a space plague. Both parties encounter the native people and trouble ensues. In an attempt to find what caused the power-loss, the Doctor, chased by the Daleks, enter the Exxilon&apos;s lost city to be able to stop the power draining phenomenon.</p>",11,11,25,"1974-02-23","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285912.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323141/doctor-who-11x11-death-to-the-daleks-part-one"),
(323142,"Death to the Daleks, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor and the MSC crew join forces with the Daleks to mine the parrinium, only to come under attack from the Exxilons.</p>",12,11,25,"1974-03-02","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285919.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323142/doctor-who-11x12-death-to-the-daleks-part-two"),
(323143,"Death to the Daleks, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor and Sarah meet up with Bellal, who helps them escape from the Daleks and explains the origin of the City.</p>",13,11,25,"1974-03-09","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285922.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323143/doctor-who-11x13-death-to-the-daleks-part-three"),
(323144,"Death to the Daleks, Part Four",766,"<p>The Doctor and Bellal continue to penetrate the City&apos;s defences while Sarah and Jill try to stop the Daleks leaving with the parrinium.</p>",14,11,25,"1974-03-16","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285932.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323144/doctor-who-11x14-death-to-the-daleks-part-four"),
(323145,"The Monster of Peladon, Part One",766,"<p>Returning to the medieval planet Peladon (50 years after &quot;The Curse of Peladon&quot;) The Doctor and Sarah find King Peladon&apos;s daughter Queen Thalira has inherited the throne and the galactic Federation is at war with Galaxy Five and The Federation requires the mineral Trisilicate that will end the war. Only to discover the miners led by the mad rebel Ettis are rebelling and refusing to work, as the ghost of the loyal best Aggedor is frightening and killing off Miners, only to discover the ghost of Aggedor is a holographic projection and the culprits are a task-force of renegade Ice Warriors led by Commander Azaxyr and traitorous federation mining engineer Eckersley who have betrayed the Federation to Galaxy Five.</p>",15,11,25,"1974-03-23","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285934.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323145/doctor-who-11x15-the-monster-of-peladon-part-one"),
(323146,"The Monster of Peladon, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor is rescued by Gebek, prompting him to try and help the miners, but his advice results in Ettis launching another attack on the armoury.</p>",16,11,25,"1974-03-30","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285938.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323146/doctor-who-11x16-the-monster-of-peladon-part-two"),
(323147,"The Monster of Peladon, Part Three",766,"<p>The Doctor and Sarah pacify Aggedor and the Doctor encourages the Queen to make peace with the miners, but Ortron soon has him under arrest again.</p>",17,11,25,"1974-04-06","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285942.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323147/doctor-who-11x17-the-monster-of-peladon-part-three"),
(323148,"The Monster of Peladon, Part Four",766,"<p>The Ice Warriors take control of the planet and force the miners to return to work but Ettis takes the opportunity to try and destroy the citadel.</p>",18,11,25,"1974-04-13","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285948.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323148/doctor-who-11x18-the-monster-of-peladon-part-four"),
(323149,"The Monster of Peladon, Part Five",766,"<p>Sarah and Alpha Centauri decide to try and alert the Federation to what the Ice Warriors are up to but first they have to escape from the throne room.</p>",19,11,25,"1974-04-20","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/285950.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323149/doctor-who-11x19-the-monster-of-peladon-part-five"),
(323150,"The Monster of Peladon, Part Six",766,"<p>The Doctor turns the Aggedor spirit against the Ice Warriors to aid the Peladonians in their battle but Eckersley attacks him with the security system.</p>",20,11,25,"1974-04-27","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/286491.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323150/doctor-who-11x20-the-monster-of-peladon-part-six"),
(323151,"Planet of the Spiders, Part One",766,"<p>While the Doctor carries out an investigation into ESP, Mike Yates asks Sarah to look into some strange goings on at a meditation centre he&apos;s attending.</p>",21,11,25,"1974-05-04","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/286492.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323151/doctor-who-11x21-planet-of-the-spiders-part-one"),
(323152,"Planet of the Spiders, Part Two",766,"<p>Lupton forms an alliance with the spider to steal the Doctor&apos;s blue crystal, while Sarah and Mike attempt to alert people to what they&apos;ve seen.</p>",22,11,25,"1974-05-11","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/286493.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323152/doctor-who-11x22-planet-of-the-spiders-part-two"),
