(323154,"Planet of the Spiders, Part Four",766,"<p>Sarah is captured by the spiders&apos; guards while the Doctor tries to help Arak and the others strike back against the spiders.</p>",24,11,25,"1974-05-25","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/286495.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323154/doctor-who-11x24-planet-of-the-spiders-part-four"),
(323155,"Planet of the Spiders, Part Five",766,"<p>The Doctor escapes from the spiders&apos; larder only to encounter the Great One, while Sarah makes a deal with the Queen Spider.</p>",25,11,25,"1974-06-01","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/286496.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323155/doctor-who-11x25-planet-of-the-spiders-part-five"),
(323156,"Planet of the Spiders, Part Six",766,"<p>K&apos;Anpo persuades the Doctor he must face his fear and return the crystal to the Great One.But first they need to get past Barnes and his men.</p>",26,11,25,"1974-06-08","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/286497.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323156/doctor-who-11x26-planet-of-the-spiders-part-six"),
(323162,"Robot, Part One",766,"<p>Can the Doctor, now in his fourth incarnation. Recover from his post regenerative trauma to save the Earth from Think Tank and their plot for world domination.</p>",1,12,25,"1974-12-28","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/85/213007.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323162/doctor-who-12x01-robot-part-one"),
