(323167,"The Ark in Space, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor&apos;s attempt to give Harry a trip in the TARDIS sees the two of them and Sarah arriving onboard space station Nerva in the far future, with some rather deadly security mechanisms.</p>",5,12,25,"1975-01-25","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/85/213020.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323167/doctor-who-12x05-the-ark-in-space-part-one"),
