(323169,"The Ark in Space, Part Three",766,"<p>Knowing that Noah has been infected by the Wirrn, the Doctor persuades Vira to halt the reviving of her people, knowing it will place them in danger as well.</p>",7,12,25,"1975-02-08","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/85/213023.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323169/doctor-who-12x07-the-ark-in-space-part-three"),
