(323191,"Planet of Evil, Part One",766,"<p>The Doctor and Sarah answer a distress call and find themselves on Zeta Minor, the last planet of the known universe, where a Morestran expedition has gone missing.</p>",5,13,25,"1975-09-27","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/286523.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323191/doctor-who-13x05-planet-of-evil-part-one"),
(323192,"Planet of Evil, Part Two",766,"<p>The Doctor realises that Zeta Minor lies on the boundary between the universes of matter and anti-matter and something on the planet won&apos;t let the Morestrans leave.</p>",6,13,25,"1975-10-04","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/114/286524.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/323192/doctor-who-13x06-planet-of-evil-part-two"),
