(13910,"The Beast Below",210,"<p>The Doctor takes Amy to the distant future where she finds Britain in space. Starship UK houses the future of the British people, as they search the stars for a new home. But as Amy explores, she encounters the terrifying Smilers and learns a deadly truth inside the Voting Booth.</p>",2,5,45,"2010-04-10","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/139/349743.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/13910/doctor-who-5x02-the-beast-below"),
