(13915,"Amy&apos;s Choice",210,"<p>It&apos;s been five years since Amy Pond traveled with the Doctor and when he lands in her garden again, on the eve of the birth of her first child, she finds herself facing a heartbreaking choice.</p>",7,5,45,"2010-05-15","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/140/350607.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/13915/doctor-who-5x07-amys-choice"),
(13916,"The Hungry Earth",210,"<p>2015: the most ambitious drilling project in history has reached deeper below the Earth&apos;s crust than man has ever gone – but now the ground itself is fighting back.</p>",8,5,45,"2010-05-22","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/140/350668.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/13916/doctor-who-5x08-the-hungry-earth"),
(13917,"Cold Blood",210,"<p>It&apos;s the most important day in the history of Earth—the dawn of a new age of harmony or the start of its final war.</p>",9,5,45,"2010-05-29","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/140/350971.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/13917/doctor-who-5x09-cold-blood"),
