(40838,"The One Where Rachel Has a Baby, Part 1",431,"<p>Rachel and Ross arrive at the hospital. Monica and Chandler decide to have a baby and right away. Mrs. Geller turns up to give Ross her mother&apos;s engagement ring; she wants Ross to marry Rachel. Joey can&apos;t understand why somebody wouldn&apos;t want to be married to Rachel. Phoebe meets a handsome stranger, but can&apos;t quite get his room number, so she gets Dr. Drake Ramoray to get it.</p>",23,8,30,"2002-05-16","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/193/484448.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/40838/friends-8x23-the-one-where-rachel-has-a-baby-part-1"),
