(1663945,"Oppressor",1825,"<p>As tensions on Ilus reach a boiling point, Holden reveals a secret. Avasarala debates Nancy Gao while an emergency on the Roci forces Alex and Naomi into action.</p>",5,4,45,"2019-12-13","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/231/577834.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1663945/the-expanse-4x05-oppressor"),
