(1663948,"The One-Eyed Man",1825,"<p>Avasarala faces fallout for the UN&apos;s military mission. Ashford and Drummer makes big decisions about their future within the OPA. A spreading illness on Ilus takes a toll on Amos. Alex and Naomi&apos;s attempt to rescue the Barb turns desperate.</p>",8,4,53,"2019-12-13","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/231/577837.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1663948/the-expanse-4x08-the-one-eyed-man"),
(1663949,"Saeculum",1825,"<p>Holden and Miller race to save Ilus. Murtry puts his endgame into motion, putting the Roci crew&apos;s lives at risk.</p>",9,4,43,"2019-12-13","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/231/577831.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1663949/the-expanse-4x09-saeculum"),
(1647593,"Cibola Burn",1825,"<p>Ashford closes in on an enemy while uncovering a dangerous plot. Avasarala faces a crossroads in her personal and political life. The Roci crew works to reestablish life on Ilus in the wake of a deadly catastrophe.</p>",10,4,49,"2019-12-13","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/231/577839.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1647593/the-expanse-4x10-cibola-burn"),
