(1945901,"Mother",1825,"<p>Naomi comes face to face with Filip. Holden and Fred turn the tables. Avasarala closes in on Marco&apos;s plot.</p>",3,5,52,"2020-12-16","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/370/926359.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1945901/the-expanse-5x03-mother"),
