(1945906,"Hard Vacuum",1825,"<p>Amos returns to Baltimore with Clarissa. On Luna, Avasarala&apos;s creates division in the UN Council. Alone and adrift, Naomi becomes a deadly lure. Drummer feels the pressure growing on all sides. The Razorback receives an unexpected message. </p>",8,5,54,"2021-01-20","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/293/733933.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1945906/the-expanse-5x08-hard-vacuum"),
(1945907,"Winnipesaukee",1825,"<p>Amos, Clarissa, and a gang of thieves work together to leave Earth. Avasarala tries to head off a brutal military strike. Drummer&apos;s new family bonds are tested as Naomi&apos;s life hangs in the balance.</p>",9,5,52,"2021-01-27","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/295/738566.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1945907/the-expanse-5x09-winnipesaukee"),
(1945908,"Nemesis Games",1825,"<p>Holden and the Roci face off against Marco&apos;s forces and Drummer, while Alex and Bobbie attempt a dangerous rescue of Naomi, and the balance of power in the Solar System shifts.</p>",10,5,56,"2021-02-03","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/295/738552.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/1945908/the-expanse-5x10-nemesis-games"),
(2189902,"Strange Dogs",1825,"<p>The tensions of war threaten to pull the Rocinante crew apart when they make a startling discovery on an asteroid. Avasarala and Bobbie contend with the devastation on Earth as Marco&apos;s rocks continue to rain down. In the Belt and on the run, Drummer and her family must make a heartbreaking decision. On Ceres, Marco and Filip&apos;s struggles turn inward.</p>",1,6,47,"2021-12-10","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/382/955413.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2189902/the-expanse-6x01-strange-dogs"),
(2190013,"Azure Dragon",1825,"<p>With an unexpected passenger aboard the Rocinante, Holden and crew undertake a dangerous mission that could shift the balance of power in the war. Drummer decides to make an uneasy alliance. Filip wrestles with his guilt.</p>",2,6,44,"2021-12-17","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/384/961946.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2190013/the-expanse-6x02-azure-dragon"),
(2190014,"Force Projection",1825,"<p>Avasarala, with the Combined Fleet of Earth and Mars, takes the war to Marco. Filip and Marco&apos;s relationship is tested. The war becomes more perilous and personal for Holden and Naomi when the Rocinante is suddenly forced into a battle.</p>",3,6,45,"2021-12-24","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/388/971226.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2190014/the-expanse-6x03-force-projection"),
(2190015,"Redoubt",1825,"<p>Holden finds himself at odds with his crew when a controversial decision is uncovered. On Ceres, Avasarala struggles to contain an escalating humanitarian crisis. Drummer&apos;s growing faction stage a daring raid with dire stakes. Filip, demoted to repair skiff duty, makes an unexpected discovery.</p>",4,6,47,"2021-12-31","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/387/968496.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2190015/the-expanse-6x04-redoubt"),
(2190016,"Why We Fight",1825,"<p>Paths converge on Ceres when Drummer and her fleet arrive to aid the relief effort. Holden tries to convince Avasarala to release crucial information that might avert catastrophe, but she has her own request of him. As Amos and Bobbie get a little R&amp;R at the station, Naomi has a difficult and long-awaited reunion.</p>",5,6,48,"2022-01-07","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/388/971224.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2190016/the-expanse-6x05-why-we-fight"),
(2190017,"Babylon&apos;s Ashes",1825,"<p>In the thrilling season finale, Inners and Belters fight side by side with the crew of the Rocinante in a last, massive, desperate battle with Marco and his Free Navy, with the fate of the Solar System, the Ring Gates, and of all humanity hanging in the balance.</p>",6,6,64,"2022-01-14","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/389/973301.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2190017/the-expanse-6x06-babylons-ashes"),
(2096438,"Leavetaking",35083,"<p>A strange noblewoman arrives in a remote mountain village, claiming one of five youths is the reincarnation of an ancient power who once destroyed the world – and will do so again, if she&apos;s not able to discover which of them it is. But they all have less time than they think.</p>",1,1,54,"2021-11-19","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/376/940919.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2096438/the-wheel-of-time-1x01-leavetaking"),
(2136155,"Shadow&apos;s Waiting",35083,"<p>Moiraine and Lan lead the four villagers to safety, unsure which is the one from the prophecy. But the friends are equally unsure about their rescuers, especially once they see how far Moiraine is willing to go for her mission – and how far astray Lan is willing to lead them.</p>",2,1,57,"2021-11-19","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/376/940922.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2136155/the-wheel-of-time-1x02-shadows-waiting"),
(2136156,"A Place of Safety",35083,"<p>Moiraine and Lan find help in an unexpected – and unwanted – quarter, as the separated villagers try to find their way back to each other, or at least to refuge. But they all soon learn how far the Dark One&apos;s reach extends, and how few they can trust on the road.</p>",3,1,58,"2021-11-19","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/376/940924.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2136156/the-wheel-of-time-1x03-a-place-of-safety"),
(2136157,"The Dragon Reborn",35083,"<p>Moiraine struggles with uncertainty while Lan struggles with their new companion. Rand wonders about Mat and Mat starts to wonder at himself. Egwene and Perrin take their first steps down a different path. An incredible new power is unleashed on the world.</p>",4,1,61,"2021-11-26","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/378/945580.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2136157/the-wheel-of-time-1x04-the-dragon-reborn"),
(2136158,"Blood Calls Blood",35083,"<p>Perrin and Egwene run into a familiar face. Mat and Rand see strange ones. Moiraine and Lan mourn their loss.</p>",5,1,60,"2021-12-03","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/380/950283.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2136158/the-wheel-of-time-1x05-blood-calls-blood"),
(2136159,"The Flame of Tar Valon",35083,"<p>Moiraine faces the consequences of her actions. Mat faces the darkness in himself. Egwene faces the most powerful woman in the world.</p>",6,1,62,"2021-12-10","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/382/955417.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2136159/the-wheel-of-time-1x06-the-flame-of-tar-valon"),
