(2516379,"Daughter of the Night",35083,"<p>Moiraine searches for Rand while Nynaeve mourns her losses.</p>",4,2,61,"2023-09-08","https://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_landscape/476/1190162.jpg","https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/2516379/the-wheel-of-time-2x04-daughter-of-the-night"),
